thumbFile: Movie - I_ Robot [263684].images\I_ Robot [263684].thumb.jpg

title: Ice Age
summary: Back when the Earth was being overrun by glaciers, and animals were scurrying to save themselves from the upcoming Ice Age, a sloth named Sid, a woolly mammoth named Manny, and a saber-toothed tiger named Diego are forced to become unlikely heroes. The three reluctantly come together when they have to return a human child to its father while braving the deadly elements of the impending Ice Age.
tagline: They came. They thawed. They conquered.
thumbFile: Movie - Ice Age [263696].images\Ice Age [263696].thumb.jpg

title: The Ice Age Adventures of Buck Wild
titleSort: Ice Age Adventures of Buck Wild
summary: Desperate for some distance from their older sister Ellie, the thrill-seeking possum brothers Crash and Eddie set out to find a place of their own, but quickly find themselves trapped in a massive cave underground. They are rescued by the one-eyed, adventure-loving, dinosaur-hunting weasel, Buck Wild, and together they must face the unruly dinosaurs who inhabit the Lost World.
tagline: Disney+ gets wild.
thumbFile: Movie - The Ice Age Adventures of Buck Wild [265003].images\The Ice Age Adventures of Buck Wild [265003].thumb.jpg

title: Ice Age: Collision Course
summary: Scrat's epic pursuit of his elusive acorn catapults him outside of Earth, where he accidentally sets off a series of cosmic events that transform and threaten the planet. To save themselves from peril, Manny, Sid, Diego, and the rest of the herd leave their home and embark on a quest full of thrills and spills, highs and lows, laughter and adventure while traveling to exotic new lands and encountering a host of colorful new characters.
tagline: One small step. One giant mess.
thumbFile: Movie - Ice Age_ Collision Course [263697].images\Ice Age_ Collision Course [263697].thumb.jpg

title: Ice Age: Continental Drift
summary: Manny, Diego, and Sid embark upon another adventure after their continent is set adrift. Using an iceberg as a ship, they encounter sea creatures and battle pirates as they explore a new world.
tagline: The end of the world is just the tip of the iceberg.
thumbFile: Movie - Ice Age_ Continental Drift [263701].images\Ice Age_ Continental Drift [263701].thumb.jpg

title: Ice Age: Dawn of the Dinosaurs
titleSort: Ice Age: Dawn of the Dinosaurs
summary: Times are changing for Manny the moody mammoth, Sid the motor mouthed sloth and Diego the crafty saber-toothed tiger. Life heats up for our heroes when they meet some new and none-too-friendly neighbors – the mighty dinosaurs.
tagline: You won't believe your ice!
thumbFile: Movie - Ice Age_ Dawn of the Dinosaurs [263703].images\Ice Age_ Dawn of the Dinosaurs [263703].thumb.jpg

title: Ice Age: The Meltdown
summary: Manny, Sid and Diego discover that the ice age is coming to an end, and join everybody for a journey to higher ground. On the trip, they discover that Manny is not in fact the last of the woolly mammoths.
tagline: Kiss Your Nuts Goodbye
thumbFile: Movie - Ice Age_ The Meltdown [263704].images\Ice Age_ The Meltdown [263704].thumb.jpg

title: Idiocracy
summary: Corporal Joe Bauers, a decidedly average American, is selected for a top-secret hibernation program but is forgotten and left to awaken to a future so incredibly moronic that he's easily the most intelligent person alive.
tagline: In the future, intelligence is extinct.
thumbFile: Movie - Idiocracy [263707].images\Idiocracy [263707].thumb.jpg

title: The Incredibles
summary: Bob Parr has given up his superhero days to log in time as an insurance adjuster and raise his three children with his formerly heroic wife in suburbia. But when he receives a mysterious assignment, it's time to get back into costume.
tagline: No gut, no glory.
thumbFile: Movie - The Incredibles [265012].images\The Incredibles [265012].thumb.jpg

title: Incredibles 2
summary: The Incredibles family takes on a new mission which involves a change in family roles: Bob Parr (Mr. Incredible) must manage the house while his wife Helen (Elastigirl) goes out to save the world.
tagline: It's time to get back to being incredible.
thumbFile: Movie - Incredibles 2 [263714].images\Incredibles 2 [263714].thumb.jpg

title: Independence Day
summary: Strange phenomena surface around the globe. The skies ignite. Terror races through the world's major cities. As these extraordinary events unfold, it becomes increasingly clear that a force of incredible magnitude has arrived. Its mission: total annihilation over the Fourth of July weekend. The last hope to stop the destruction is an unlikely group of people united by fate and unimaginable circumstances.
tagline: The question of whether or not we are alone in the universe has been answered.
thumbFile: Movie - Independence Day [263715].images\Independence Day [263715].thumb.jpg

title: Indiana Jones and the Kingdom of the Crystal Skull
titleSort: Indiana Jones and the Kingdom of the Crystal Skull
summary: Set during the Cold War, the Soviets—led by sword-wielding Irina Spalko—are in search of a crystal skull which has supernatural powers related to a mystical Lost City of Gold. Indy is coerced to head to Peru at the behest of a young man whose friend—and Indy's colleague—Professor Oxley has been captured for his knowledge of the skull's whereabouts.
tagline: The adventure continues...
thumbFile: Movie - Indiana Jones and the Kingdom of the Crystal Skull [263721].images\Indiana Jones and the Kingdom of the Crystal Skull [263721].thumb.jpg

title: Indiana Jones and the Last Crusade
titleSort: Indiana Jones and the Last Crusade
summary: An art collector appeals to Indiana Jones to embark on a search for the Holy Grail. He learns that another archaeologist has disappeared while searching for the precious goblet, and the missing man is his own father, Dr. Henry Jones. The artifact is much harder to find than they expected, and its powers are too much for those impure of heart.
tagline: The man with the hat is back. And this time, he's bringing his Dad.
thumbFile: Movie - Indiana Jones and the Last Crusade [263723].images\Indiana Jones and the Last Crusade [263723].thumb.jpg

title: Indiana Jones and the Temple of Doom
titleSort: Indiana Jones and the Temple of Doom
summary: After arriving in India, Indiana Jones is asked by a desperate village to find a mystical stone. He agrees – and stumbles upon a secret cult plotting a terrible plan in the catacombs of an ancient palace.
tagline: If adventure has a name... it must be Indiana Jones.
thumbFile: Movie - Indiana Jones and the Temple of Doom [263729].images\Indiana Jones and the Temple of Doom [263729].thumb.jpg

title: Inglourious Basterds
summary: In Nazi-occupied France during World War II, a group of Jewish-American soldiers known as "The Basterds" are chosen specifically to spread fear throughout the Third Reich by scalping and brutally killing Nazis. The Basterds, lead by Lt. Aldo Raine soon cross paths with a French-Jewish teenage girl who runs a movie theater in Paris which is targeted by the soldiers.
tagline: A basterd's work is never done.
thumbFile: Movie - Inglourious Basterds [263732].images\Inglourious Basterds [263732].thumb.jpg

title: Inside Out
summary: When 11-year-old Riley moves to a new city, her Emotions team up to help her through the transition. Joy, Fear, Anger, Disgust and Sadness work together, but when Joy and Sadness get lost, they must journey through unfamiliar places to get back home.
tagline: Meet the little voices inside your head.
thumbFile: Movie - Inside Out [263736].images\Inside Out [263736].thumb.jpg

title: Inside Out 2
summary: A sequel that features Riley entering puberty and experiencing brand new, more complex emotions as a result. As Riley tries to adapt to her teenage years, her old emotions try to adapt to the possibility of being replaced.
tagline: Make room for new emotions.
thumbFile: Movie - Inside Out 2 [263737].images\Inside Out 2 [263737].thumb.jpg

title: Instant Family
summary: When Pete and Ellie decide to start a family, they stumble into the world of foster care adoption. They hope to take in one small child but when they meet three siblings, including a rebellious 15 year old girl, they find themselves speeding from zero to three kids overnight.
tagline: Just add chaos, laughter, awkwardness, mistakes, love...
thumbFile: Movie - Instant Family [263741].images\Instant Family [263741].thumb.jpg

title: Interstellar
summary: When Earth becomes uninhabitable in the future, a farmer and ex-NASA pilot, Joseph Cooper, is tasked to pilot a spacecraft, along with a team of researchers, to find a new planet for humans.
tagline: Mankind was born on Earth. It was never meant to die here.
thumbFile: Movie - Interstellar [263742].images\Interstellar [263742].thumb.jpg

title: The Interview
summary: Dave Skylark and his producer Aaron Rapaport run the celebrity tabloid show "Skylark Tonight". When they land an interview with a surprise fan, North Korean dictator Jong-Un Kim, they are recruited by the CIA to assassinate him.
tagline: The Film Hackers Tried To Get Banned
thumbFile: Movie - The Interview [265013].images\The Interview [265013].thumb.jpg

title: The Invention of Lying
summary: A comedy set in a world where no one has ever lied, until a writer seizes the opportunity for personal gain.
tagline: In a world where everyone can only tell the truth... This guy can lie.
thumbFile: Movie - The Invention of Lying [265014].images\The Invention of Lying [265014].thumb.jpg

title: The Iron Giant
summary: This is the story of a nine-year-old boy named Hogarth Hughes who makes friends with an innocent alien giant robot that came from outer space. Meanwhile, a paranoid U.S. Government agent named Kent Mansley arrives in town, determined to destroy the giant at all costs. It's up to Hogarth to protect him by keeping him at Dean McCoppin's place in the junkyard.
tagline: It came from outer space!
thumbFile: Movie - The Iron Giant [265023].images\The Iron Giant [265023].thumb.jpg

title: Iron Man
summary: After being held captive in an Afghan cave, billionaire engineer Tony Stark creates a unique weaponized suit of armor to fight evil.
tagline: Heroes aren't born. They're built.
thumbFile: Movie - Iron Man [263745].images\Iron Man [263745].thumb.jpg

title: Iron Man 2
summary: With the world now aware of his dual life as the armored superhero Iron Man, billionaire inventor Tony Stark faces pressure from the government, the press, and the public to share his technology with the military. Unwilling to let go of his invention, Stark, along with Pepper Potts, and James "Rhodey" Rhodes at his side, must forge new alliances - and confront powerful enemies.
tagline: It's not the armor that makes the hero, but the man inside.
thumbFile: Movie - Iron Man 2 [263757].images\Iron Man 2 [263757].thumb.jpg

title: Iron Man 3
summary: When Tony Stark's world is torn apart by a formidable terrorist called the Mandarin, he starts an odyssey of rebuilding and retribution.
tagline: Unleash the power behind the armor.
thumbFile: Movie - Iron Man 3 [263767].images\Iron Man 3 [263767].thumb.jpg

title: Isle of Dogs
summary: An outbreak of dog flu has spread through the city of Megasaki, Japan, and Mayor Kobayashi has demanded all dogs to be sent to Trash Island. On the island, a young boy named Atari sets out to find his lost dog, Spots, with the help of five other dogs... with many obstacles along the way.
tagline: Welcome to the Isle of Dogs.
thumbFile: Movie - Isle of Dogs [263768].images\Isle of Dogs [263768].thumb.jpg

title: It
summary: In the Town of Derry, the local kids are disappearing one by one. In a place known as 'The Barrens', a group of seven kids are united by their horrifying and strange encounters with an evil clown and their determination to kill It.
tagline: You’ll float too.
thumbFile: Movie - It [263776].images\It [263776].thumb.jpg

title: It Chapter Two
summary: 27 years after overcoming the malevolent supernatural entity Pennywise, the former members of the Losers' Club, who have grown up and moved away from Derry, are brought back together by a devastating phone call.
tagline: It ends
thumbFile: Movie - It Chapter Two [263780].images\It Chapter Two [263780].thumb.jpg

title: It Follows
summary: For 19-year-old Jay, autumn should be about school, boys, and weekends out at the lake. But after a seemingly innocent sexual encounter, she is plagued by strange visions and the inescapable sense that someone, or something, is following her. Faced with this burden, Jay and her friends must find a way to escape the horrors that seem to be only a few steps behind.
tagline: It doesn't think, it doesn't feel, it doesn't give up.
thumbFile: Movie - It Follows [263781].images\It Follows [263781].thumb.jpg

title: Jackass 3D
summary: Johnny Knoxville, Bam Margera, Steve-O, Wee Man and the rest of their fearless and foolhardy friends take part in another round of outrageous pranks and stunts. In addition to standing in the path of a charging bull, launching themselves into the air and crashing through various objects, the guys perform in segments such as "Sweatsuit Cocktail," "Beehive Tetherball" and "Lamborghini Tooth Pull."
tagline: 3 Times the Laughs. 3 Times the Stupid. 3 Times the Pain.
thumbFile: Movie - Jackass 3D [263782].images\Jackass 3D [263782].thumb.jpg

title: Jackass Number Two
summary: Jackass Number Two is a compilation of various stunts, pranks and skits, and essentially has no plot. Chris Pontius, Johnny Knoxville, Steve-O, Bam Margera, and the whole crew return to the screen to raise the stakes higher than ever before.
tagline: Guess who just made number two?
thumbFile: Movie - Jackass Number Two [263788].images\Jackass Number Two [263788].thumb.jpg

title: Jackass Presents: Bad Grandpa
summary: 86-year-old Irving Zisman takes a trip from Nebraska to North Carolina to take his 8 year-old grandson, Billy, back to his real father.
tagline: Real people. Real reactions. Real messed up.
thumbFile: Movie - Jackass Presents_ Bad Grandpa [263794].images\Jackass Presents_ Bad Grandpa [263794].thumb.jpg

title: James and the Giant Peach
summary: An orphan who lives with his two cruel aunts befriends anthropomorphic bugs who live inside a giant peach, and they embark on a journey to New York City.
tagline: Adventures this big don't grow on trees.
thumbFile: Movie - James and the Giant Peach [263797].images\James and the Giant Peach [263797].thumb.jpg

title: Jason Goes to Hell
originalTitle: Jason Goes to Hell: The Final Friday
summary: The secret of Jason's evil is revealed. It is up to the last remaining descendant of the Voorhees family to stop Jason before he becomes immortal and unstoppable. This is the final (?) battle to end Jason's reign of terror forever.
tagline: Evil has finally found a home.
thumbFile: Movie - Jason Goes to Hell [263801].images\Jason Goes to Hell [263801].thumb.jpg

title: Jason X
summary: Jason Voorhees is cryogenically frozen at the beginning of the 21st century, and is discovered in the 25th century and taken to space. He gets thawed, and begins stalking and killing the crew of the spaceship that's transporting him.
tagline: Evil gets an upgrade.
thumbFile: Movie - Jason X [263804].images\Jason X [263804].thumb.jpg

title: Jaws
summary: When the seaside community of Amity finds itself under attack by a dangerous great white shark, the town's chief of police, a young marine biologist, and a grizzled hunter embark on a desperate quest to destroy the beast before it strikes again.
tagline: The terrifying motion picture from the terrifying No.1 best seller.
thumbFile: Movie - Jaws [265490].images\Jaws [265490].thumb.jpg

title: Jigsaw
summary: It has been over a decade since Jigsaw died. However, after a new series of deaths occurs, police find themselves chasing after the original Jigsaw - John Kramer. Could John Kramer still be alive or is another killer out there with a different motive?
tagline: The game continues.
thumbFile: Movie - Jigsaw [263809].images\Jigsaw [263809].thumb.jpg

title: Jimmy Neutron: Boy Genius
summary: Jimmy Neutron is a boy genius and way ahead of his friends, but when it comes to being cool, he's a little behind. All until one day when his parents, and parents all over Earth are kidnapped by aliens, it's up to him to lead all the children of the world to rescue their parents.
tagline: A little genius becomes a big hero.
thumbFile: Movie - Jimmy Neutron_ Boy Genius [263810].images\Jimmy Neutron_ Boy Genius [263810].thumb.jpg

title: Jingle All the Way
summary: A father vows to get his son a Turbo Man action figure for Christmas. However, every store is sold out, and he must travel all over town and compete with everybody else in order to find one.
tagline: Two dads, one toy, no prisoners.
thumbFile: Movie - Jingle All the Way [267834].images\Jingle All the Way [267834].thumb.jpg

title: Joe Dirt
summary: Joe Dirt is a janitor with a mullet hairdo, acid-washed jeans and a dream to find the parents that he lost at the Grand Canyon when he was a belligerent, trailer park-raised eight-year-old. Now, blasting Van Halen in his jacked-up economy car, the irrepressibly optimistic Joe hits the road alone in search of his folks.
tagline: He came. He cleaned. He conquered.
thumbFile: Movie - Joe Dirt [263811].images\Joe Dirt [263811].thumb.jpg

title: Joe Dirt 2: Beautiful Loser
summary: Many of the original actors reprise their roles as the Iconic acquaintances to the perpetual underdog of the film's namesake. According to Spade this film will be aired directly to the website Crackle in the summer of 2015. He also stated that fan pressure compelled him to don the mullet again, as the original encroaches on cult status.
tagline: Go Hick Yourself
thumbFile: Movie - Joe Dirt 2_ Beautiful Loser [263812].images\Joe Dirt 2_ Beautiful Loser [263812].thumb.jpg

title: John Mulaney & the Sack Lunch Bunch
titleSort: John Mulaney & the Sack Lunch Bunch
summary: John Mulaney and his kid pals tackle existential topics for all ages with catchy songs, comedy sketches and special guests in a nostalgic variety special.
tagline: A children's musical comedy special from a man with neither children nor musical ability
thumbFile: Movie - John Mulaney _ the Sack Lunch Bunch [263815].images\John Mulaney _ the Sack Lunch Bunch [263815].thumb.jpg

title: John Mulaney: Baby J
summary: A chaotic intervention. An action packed stay in rehab. After a weird couple of years, John Mulaney comes out swinging in his return to the stage.
tagline: A wide-ranging conversation
thumbFile: Movie - John Mulaney_ Baby J [263818].images\John Mulaney_ Baby J [263818].thumb.jpg

title: John Mulaney: Kid Gorgeous at Radio City
titleSort: John Mulaney: Kid Gorgeous at Radio City
summary: John Mulaney relays his childhood and Saturday Night Live (1975), eviscerates the value of college, and laments getting older in this comedy special. Other topics include the church, his family, President Trump and pedophiles abducting kids.
thumbFile: Movie - John Mulaney_ Kid Gorgeous at Radio City [263819].images\John Mulaney_ Kid Gorgeous at Radio City [263819].thumb.jpg

title: John Mulaney: New in Town
summary: Comedian John Mulaney talks about his milk toast boyish looks, his childhood, his Jewish girlfriend, his gayish charm, his favorite TV shows, Ice-T, a homeless person he met in N.Y., and a prostate exam with Batman.
thumbFile: Movie - John Mulaney_ New in Town [263824].images\John Mulaney_ New in Town [263824].thumb.jpg

title: John Mulaney: The Comeback Kid
summary: Armed with boyish charm and a sharp wit, the former SNL writer offers sly takes on marriage, his beef with babies and the time he met Bill Clinton.
thumbFile: Movie - John Mulaney_ The Comeback Kid [263826].images\John Mulaney_ The Comeback Kid [263826].thumb.jpg

title: John Wick
summary: John Wick is a former hitman grieving the loss of his true love. When his home is broken into, robbed, and his dog killed, he is forced to return to action to exact revenge.
tagline: Don't set him off.
thumbFile: Movie - John Wick [263827].images\John Wick [263827].thumb.jpg

title: John Wick: Chapter 2
summary: John Wick is forced out of retirement by a former associate looking to seize control of a shadowy international assassins’ guild. Bound by a blood oath to aid him, Wick travels to Rome and does battle against some of the world’s most dangerous killers.
tagline: Never stab the devil in the back!
thumbFile: Movie - John Wick_ Chapter 2 [263829].images\John Wick_ Chapter 2 [263829].thumb.jpg

title: John Wick: Chapter 3 - Parabellum
summary: In this third installment of the adrenaline-fueled action franchise, skilled assassin John Wick (Keanu Reeves) returns with a $14 million price tag on his head and an army of bounty-hunting killers on his trail. After killing a member of the shadowy international assassin's guild, the High Table, John Wick is excommunicado, but the world's most ruthless hit men and women await his every turn.
tagline: If you want peace, prepare for war.
thumbFile: Movie - John Wick_ Chapter 3 - Parabellum [263830].images\John Wick_ Chapter 3 - Parabellum [263830].thumb.jpg

title: John Wick: Chapter 4
summary: John Wick uncovers a path to defeating The High Table. But before he can earn his freedom, Wick must face off against a new enemy with powerful alliances across the globe and forces that turn old friends into foes.
tagline: No way back, one way out.
thumbFile: Movie - John Wick_ Chapter 4 [263834].images\John Wick_ Chapter 4 [263834].thumb.jpg

title: Jojo Rabbit
summary: A World War II satire that follows a lonely German boy named Jojo (Roman Griffin Davis) whose world view is turned upside down when he discovers his single mother (Scarlett Johansson) is hiding a young Jewish girl (Thomasin McKenzie) in their attic. Aided only by his idiotic imaginary friend, Adolf Hitler (Taika Waititi), Jojo must confront his blind nationalism.
tagline: It's definitely not a good time to be a Nazi.
thumbFile: Movie - Jojo Rabbit [263835].images\Jojo Rabbit [263835].thumb.jpg

title: Joker
summary: Arthur Fleck, a party clown and a failed stand-up comedian, leads an impoverished life with his ailing mother. However, when society shuns him and brands him as a freak, he decides to embrace the life of chaos in Gotham City.
tagline: Put on a happy face.
thumbFile: Movie - Joker [263840].images\Joker [263840].thumb.jpg

title: Journey 2: The Mysterious Island
summary: Sean Anderson partners with his mom's husband on a mission to find his grandfather, who is thought to be missing on a mythical island.
tagline: Believe the Impossible. Discover the Incredible.
thumbFile: Movie - Journey 2_ The Mysterious Island [263844].images\Journey 2_ The Mysterious Island [263844].thumb.jpg

title: Journey to the Center of the Earth
titleSort: Journey to the Center of the Earth
summary: On a quest to find out what happened to his missing brother, a scientist, his nephew and their mountain guide discover a fantastic and dangerous lost world in the center of the earth.
tagline: Same Planet. Different World.
thumbFile: Movie - Journey to the Center of the Earth [263845].images\Journey to the Center of the Earth [263845].thumb.jpg

title: Judy Moody and the Not Bummer Summer
titleSort: Judy Moody and the Not Bummer Summer
summary: Young Judy Moody is very excited to have the most thrilling summer of her life with her brother Stink who is a huge believer of Bigfoot. Her goal is to get as much thrill points as possible for every dare she does on her list of summer dares.
tagline: Supermegatotally thrilladelic
thumbFile: Movie - Judy Moody and the Not Bummer Summer [263854].images\Judy Moody and the Not Bummer Summer [263854].thumb.jpg

title: Jumanji
summary: When siblings Judy and Peter discover an enchanted board game that opens the door to a magical world, they unwittingly invite Alan -- an adult who's been trapped inside the game for 26 years -- into their living room. Alan's only hope for freedom is to finish the game, which proves risky as all three find themselves running from giant rhinoceroses, evil monkeys and other terrifying creatures.
tagline: Roll the dice and unleash the excitement!
thumbFile: Movie - Jumanji [263855].images\Jumanji [263855].thumb.jpg

title: Jumanji: The Next Level
summary: In Jumanji: The Next Level, the gang is back but the game has changed. As they return to rescue one of their own, the players will have to brave parts unknown from arid deserts to snowy mountains, to escape the world's most dangerous game.
tagline: Everything will change.
thumbFile: Movie - Jumanji_ The Next Level [263861].images\Jumanji_ The Next Level [263861].thumb.jpg

title: Jumanji: Welcome to the Jungle
summary: Four teenagers in detention discover an old video game console with a game they’ve never heard of. When they decide to play, they are immediately sucked into the jungle world of Jumanji in the bodies of their avatars. They’ll have to complete the adventure of their lives filled with fun, thrills and danger or be stuck in the game forever!
tagline: The game has evolved.
thumbFile: Movie - Jumanji_ Welcome to the Jungle [263865].images\Jumanji_ Welcome to the Jungle [263865].thumb.jpg

title: The Jungle Book
summary: The boy Mowgli makes his way to the man-village with Bagheera, the wise panther. Along the way he meets jazzy King Louie, the hypnotic snake Kaa and the lovable, happy-go-lucky bear Baloo, who teaches Mowgli "The Bare Necessities" of life and the true meaning of friendship.
tagline: The Jungle is JUMPIN'!
thumbFile: Movie - The Jungle Book [265024].images\The Jungle Book [265024].thumb.jpg

title: The Jungle Book
summary: A man-cub named Mowgli fostered by wolves. After a threat from the tiger Shere Khan, Mowgli is forced to flee the jungle, by which he embarks on a journey of self discovery with the help of the panther, Bagheera and the free-spirited bear, Baloo.
tagline: The legend will never be the same.
thumbFile: Movie - The Jungle Book [265026].images\The Jungle Book [265026].thumb.jpg

title: Jungle Cruise
summary: Dr. Lily Houghton enlists the aid of wisecracking skipper Frank Wolff to take her down the Amazon in his dilapidated boat. Together, they search for an ancient tree that holds the power to heal – a discovery that will change the future of medicine.
tagline: The myth is real.
thumbFile: Movie - Jungle Cruise [263867].images\Jungle Cruise [263867].thumb.jpg

title: Juno
summary: Faced with an unplanned pregnancy, an offbeat young woman makes a selfless decision regarding the unborn child.
tagline: A comedy about growing up… and the bumps along the way.
thumbFile: Movie - Juno [263879].images\Juno [263879].thumb.jpg

title: Jurassic Park
summary: A wealthy entrepreneur secretly creates a theme park featuring living dinosaurs drawn from prehistoric DNA. Before opening day, he invites a team of experts and his two eager grandchildren to experience the park and help calm anxious investors. However, the park is anything but amusing as the security systems go off-line and the dinosaurs escape.
tagline: An adventure 65 million years in the making.
thumbFile: Movie - Jurassic Park [263880].images\Jurassic Park [263880].thumb.jpg

title: Jurassic Park III
summary: In need of funds for research, Dr. Alan Grant accepts a large sum of money to accompany Paul and Amanda Kirby on an aerial tour of the infamous Isla Sorna. It isn't long before all hell breaks loose and the stranded wayfarers must fight for survival as a host of new -- and even more deadly -- dinosaurs try to make snacks of them.
tagline: This time, it's not just a walk in the park!
thumbFile: Movie - Jurassic Park III [263890].images\Jurassic Park III [263890].thumb.jpg

title: Jurassic World
summary: Twenty-two years after the original Jurassic Park failed, the new park, also known as Jurassic World, is open for business. After years of studying genetics, the scientists on the park genetically engineer a new breed of dinosaur, the Indominus rex. When everything goes horribly wrong, will our heroes make it off the island?
tagline: The park is open.
thumbFile: Movie - Jurassic World [263896].images\Jurassic World [263896].thumb.jpg

title: Jurassic World Dominion
summary: After surviving the destruction of Isla Nubla, Owen Grady and Claire Dearing took in young Maisie Lockwood. They've been living under the radar to protect Maisie, but she feels like a prisoner. When Maisie goes missing, Owen and Claire set out to find her, and eventually confront Lewis Dodgson, owner of Biosyn. Paleobotanist Ellie Sattler, Paleontologist Alan Grant, and Chaotician Ian Malcolm set out to expose Dodgson's schemes.
tagline: The epic conclusion of the Jurassic era.
thumbFile: Movie - Jurassic World Dominion [263898].images\Jurassic World Dominion [263898].thumb.jpg

title: Jurassic World: Fallen Kingdom
summary: Three years after the Jurassic World theme park was closed down, Owen and Claire return to Isla Nublar to save the dinosaurs when they learn that a once dormant volcano on the island is active and is threatening to extinguish all life there. Along the way, Owen sets out to find Blue, his lead raptor, and discovers a conspiracy that could disrupt the natural order of the entire planet. Life has found a way, again.
tagline: The park is gone.
thumbFile: Movie - Jurassic World_ Fallen Kingdom [263901].images\Jurassic World_ Fallen Kingdom [263901].thumb.jpg

title: Just Go with It
summary: Danny (Adam Sandler) must engage Katherine (Jennifer Aniston), his faithful assistant, to pretend to be his soon to be ex-wife. Danny must pretend that he is married, because he lied to his dream girl, Palmer (Brooklyn Decker) the most gorgeous woman in the world. To keep the woman he loves, covering up one lie soon turns into many lies.
tagline: Sometimes a guy's best wingman... is a wingwoman
thumbFile: Movie - Just Go with It [263907].images\Just Go with It [263907].thumb.jpg

title: The Karate Kid
summary: Recently relocated from NJ to LA, Daniel becomes the target of a gang of Cobra Kai dojo students. When Mr. Miyagi saves him with expert Karate skills, Daniel convinces him to teach him to defend himself, and put his bullies in their place.
tagline: He taught him the secret to karate lies in the mind and heart. Not in the hands.
thumbFile: Movie - The Karate Kid [265027].images\The Karate Kid [265027].thumb.jpg

title: The Karate Kid
summary: Work causes a single mother to move to China with her young son; in his new home, the boy embraces kung fu, taught to him by a master.
tagline: A Challenge He Never Imagined. A Teacher He Never Expected.
thumbFile: Movie - The Karate Kid [265034].images\The Karate Kid [265034].thumb.jpg

title: The Karate Kid Part II
summary: Daniel accompanies his mentor, Mr. Miyagi, to Miyagi's childhood home in Okinawa. Miyagi visits his dying father and confronts his old rival, while Daniel falls in love and inadvertently makes a new rival of his own.
tagline: This time, the combat is real.
thumbFile: Movie - The Karate Kid Part II [265040].images\The Karate Kid Part II [265040].thumb.jpg

title: The Karate Kid Part III
summary: Ostracised villain John Kreese attempts to gain revenge on Daniel and Miyagi, with the help of a Vietnam War comrade, the wealthy owner of a toxic waste disposal business.
tagline: First it was teacher to student. Then it was father to son. Now, it's man to man.
thumbFile: Movie - The Karate Kid Part III [265045].images\The Karate Kid Part III [265045].thumb.jpg

title: Kevin Hart: I'm a Grown Little Man
titleSort: Kevin Hart: I'm a Grown Little Man
summary: Fresh off the heels of appearing in movies like Superhero Movie and The 40 Year-Old Virgin, fast-talking comedian Kevin Hart stars in this live stand-up performance where he makes fun of everything and everybody - especially himself.
thumbFile: Movie - Kevin Hart_ I_m a Grown Little Man [263908].images\Kevin Hart_ I_m a Grown Little Man [263908].thumb.jpg

title: Kevin Hart: Irresponsible
summary: Stand-up comedian Kevin Hart talks about his family, travel and a year full of reckless behavior in front of a live sold-out crowd in London.
thumbFile: Movie - Kevin Hart_ Irresponsible [263914].images\Kevin Hart_ Irresponsible [263914].thumb.jpg

title: Kevin Hart: Laugh at My Pain
titleSort: Kevin Hart: Laugh at My Pain
summary: Experience the show that quickly became a national phenomenon, and get an up close and personal look at Kevin Hart back in Philly, where he began his journey to become one of the funniest comedians of all time. You will laugh 'til it hurts.
tagline: Alright! Alright! Alright!
thumbFile: Movie - Kevin Hart_ Laugh at My Pain [263924].images\Kevin Hart_ Laugh at My Pain [263924].thumb.jpg

title: Kevin Hart: Let Me Explain
summary: Kevin is throwing a celebration party, but guests tell him that he has changed since his divorce. He tries to explain himself, but they will not let him, so he decides to do a show at Madison Square Garden letting him explain, which sold out with 30,000 people. The film also shows performances of his sold-out shows from all around the world..
tagline: Witness the rise of a legend
thumbFile: Movie - Kevin Hart_ Let Me Explain [263926].images\Kevin Hart_ Let Me Explain [263926].thumb.jpg

title: Kevin Hart: Reality Check
summary: Things are about to get real in this unforgettable night of comedy. Comedian Kevin Hart is as funny as ever as he processes his growing family, fame, mentions on Black Twitter, and more. Hart returns for his first stand-up special in three years with a bang, performing from Resort World in Las Vegas while cracking up a live sold-out crowd through candid conversation. Pure honesty inspires genuine humor in this tell-all comedy special.
tagline: Kill ’em with comedy.
thumbFile: Movie - Kevin Hart_ Reality Check [263927].images\Kevin Hart_ Reality Check [263927].thumb.jpg

title: Kevin Hart: Seriously Funny
summary: "Seriously Funny" stars Kevin Hart performing in front of a sold out crowd live from Cleveland, Ohio - where he delivers his hilarious and unique brand of comedy. In this unforgettable night of comedy, Kevin is in rare form and funny as ever!
thumbFile: Movie - Kevin Hart_ Seriously Funny [263928].images\Kevin Hart_ Seriously Funny [263928].thumb.jpg

title: Kevin Hart: What Now All Access
titleSort: Kevin Hart: What Now All Access
summary: An exclusive behind-the-scenes look at Kevin Hart's 2016 record-breaking "What Now?" international stand-up tour. With unparalleled access, this documentary takes you on tour and inside the superstar’s life to reveal a side of him you’ve never seen before.
tagline: The comedy event of the year.
thumbFile: Movie - Kevin Hart_ What Now All Access [263929].images\Kevin Hart_ What Now All Access [263929].thumb.jpg

title: Kick-Ass
summary: Dave Lizewski is an unnoticed high school student and comic book fan with a few friends and who lives alone with his father. His life is not very difficult and his personal trials not that overwhelming; however, one day he makes the simple decision to become a super-hero, even though he has no powers or training.
tagline: Shut up. Kick-ass.
thumbFile: Movie - Kick-Ass [263932].images\Kick-Ass [263932].thumb.jpg

title: Kick-Ass 2
summary: Following Kick-Ass' heroics, other citizens are inspired to become masked crusaders, but Red Mist leads his own group of evil super-villains to get revenge, kill Kick-Ass, and destroy everything he stands for.
tagline: You Can't Fight Your Destiny.
thumbFile: Movie - Kick-Ass 2 [263936].images\Kick-Ass 2 [263936].thumb.jpg

title: Kill Bill: Vol. 1
summary: Four years after taking a bullet in the head at her own wedding, The Bride emerges from a coma and decides it's time for payback... with a vengeance. Having been gunned down by her former boss Bill and his deadly squad of international assassins, it's a kill-or-be-killed fight she didn't start, but is determined to finish.
tagline: A roaring rampage of revenge.
thumbFile: Movie - Kill Bill_ Vol. 1 [263938].images\Kill Bill_ Vol. 1 [263938].thumb.jpg

title: Kill Bill: Vol. 2
summary: Having already crossed two names from her Death List, the Bride resumes her quest for justice, taking aim at Budd and Elle Driver, the only survivors from the squad of assassins who betrayed her four years earlier. It's all leading up to the ultimate confrontation with Bill The Bride's former master and the man who ordered her execution.
tagline: The bride is back for the final cut.
thumbFile: Movie - Kill Bill_ Vol. 2 [263944].images\Kill Bill_ Vol. 2 [263944].thumb.jpg

title: The King of Staten Island
summary: Scott has been a case of arrested development since his firefighter dad died. He spends his days smoking weed and dreaming of being a tattoo artist until events force him to grapple with his grief and take his first steps forward in life.
tagline: An aspiring comedian is stuck living with his mom in Staten Island, N.Y. following the events of September 11th.
thumbFile: Movie - The King of Staten Island [265050].images\The King of Staten Island [265050].thumb.jpg

title: The King's Man
summary: In the early years of the 20th century, the Kingsman agency is formed to stand against a cabal plotting a war to wipe out millions.
tagline: Witness the bloody origin.
thumbFile: Movie - The King_s Man [265049].images\The King_s Man [265049].thumb.jpg

title: Kingdom of the Planet of the Apes
titleSort: Kingdom of the Planet of the Apes
summary: Many years after the reign of Caesar, a young ape goes on a journey that will lead him to question everything he's been taught about the past and make choices that will define a future for apes and humans alike.
tagline: No one can stop the reign.
thumbFile: Movie - Kingdom of the Planet of the Apes [263948].images\Kingdom of the Planet of the Apes [263948].thumb.jpg

title: Kingsman: The Golden Circle
summary: After the Kingsman's headquarters is destroyed and the world is held hostage, an allied spy organization in the United States is discovered. These two elite secret agencies must band together to defeat a common enemy.
tagline: A proper spy movie.
thumbFile: Movie - Kingsman_ The Golden Circle [263950].images\Kingsman_ The Golden Circle [263950].thumb.jpg

title: Kingsman: The Secret Service
summary: A super-secret organization recruits an unrefined but promising street kid into the agency's ultra-competitive training program just as a dire global threat emerges from a twisted tech genius. A phenomenal cast, including ACADEMY AWARD® Winners Colin Firth and Michael Caine and OSCAR® Nominee Samuel L. Jackson, leads this action-packed spy-thriller directed by Matthew Vaughn (X-Men: First Class).
tagline: Manners maketh man.
thumbFile: Movie - Kingsman_ The Secret Service [263952].images\Kingsman_ The Secret Service [263952].thumb.jpg

title: Knowing
summary: A teacher opens a time capsule that has been dug up at his son's elementary school; in it are some chilling predictions -- some that have already occurred and others that are about to -- that lead him to believe his family plays a role in the events that are about to unfold.
tagline: What happens when the numbers run out?
thumbFile: Movie - Knowing [263956].images\Knowing [263956].thumb.jpg

title: Kong: Skull Island
summary: A washed up monster chaser convinces the U.S. Government to fund a trip to an unexplored island in the South Pacific. Under the guise of geological research, the team travels to "Skull Island". Upon arrival, the group discover that their mission may be complicated by the wildlife which inhabits the island. The beautiful vistas and deadly creatures create a visually stunning experience that is sure to keep your attention.
tagline: All hail the king
thumbFile: Movie - Kong_ Skull Island [263965].images\Kong_ Skull Island [263965].thumb.jpg

title: Kung Fu Panda
summary: To everyone's surprise, including his own, Po, an overweight, clumsy panda, is chosen as protector of the Valley of Peace. His suitability will soon be tested as the valley's arch-enemy is on his way.
tagline: Prepare for awesomeness.
thumbFile: Movie - Kung Fu Panda [263969].images\Kung Fu Panda [263969].thumb.jpg

title: Kung Fu Panda 2
summary: After a year of being the dragon warrior, obesitized but fearless Po (Black) is a hero in China along with Crane (Cross), Mantis (Rogen), Monkey (Chan), Viper (Liu), Tigress (Jolie), and Shifu (Hoffman). But trouble pops out when villian Shen (Oldman) begins chaos. Everybody is ready to fight, but Po is unprepared when he learns Shen was his enemy in his infancy.
tagline: Twice the awesomeness.
thumbFile: Movie - Kung Fu Panda 2 [263970].images\Kung Fu Panda 2 [263970].thumb.jpg

title: Kung Fu Panda 3
summary: When Po's long-lost panda father suddenly reappears, the reunited duo travels to a secret panda paradise to meet scores of hilarious new panda characters. But when the supernatural villain Kai begins to sweep across China defeating all the kung fu masters, Po must do the impossible-learn to train a village full of his fun-loving, clumsy brethren to become the ultimate band of Kung Fu Pandas.
tagline: Grab destiny by the rice dumplings.
thumbFile: Movie - Kung Fu Panda 3 [263984].images\Kung Fu Panda 3 [263984].thumb.jpg

title: Kung Fu Panda 4
summary: After Po is tapped to become the Spiritual Leader of the Valley of Peace, he needs to find and train a new Dragon Warrior, while a wicked sorceress plans to re-summon all the master villains whom Po has vanquished to the spirit realm.
tagline: The "dragon" returns.
thumbFile: Movie - Kung Fu Panda 4 [263985].images\Kung Fu Panda 4 [263985].thumb.jpg

title: Labyrinth
summary: When teen Sarah is forced to babysit her half-brother Toby, she summons Jareth the Goblin King to take him away. When he is actually kidnapped, Sarah is given just thirteen hours to solve a labyrinth and rescue him.
tagline: Where everything seems possible and nothing is what it seems.
thumbFile: Movie - Labyrinth [263986].images\Labyrinth [263986].thumb.jpg

title: Lady and the Tramp
summary: Lady, a golden cocker spaniel, meets up with a mongrel dog who calls himself the Tramp. He is obviously from the wrong side of town, but happenings at Lady's home make her decide to travel with him for a while. This turns out to be a bad move, as no dog is above the law.
tagline: She's from the leash and license set... he's footloose and collar free!
thumbFile: Movie - Lady and the Tramp [263989].images\Lady and the Tramp [263989].thumb.jpg

title: The Lego Batman Movie
summary: A cooler-than-ever Bruce Wayne must deal with the usual suspects as they plan to rule Gotham City, while discovering that he has accidentally adopted a teenage orphan who wishes to become his sidekick.
tagline: Always be yourself...unless you can be Batman.
thumbFile: Movie - The Lego Batman Movie [265054].images\The Lego Batman Movie [265054].thumb.jpg

title: The Lego Movie
summary: The LEGO Movie is a 3D animated film which follows lead character, Emmet, a completely ordinary LEGO mini-figure who is identified as the most "extraordinary person" and the key to saving the Lego universe. Emmet and his friends go on an epic journey to stop the evil tyrant, Lord Business.
tagline: The story of a nobody who saved everybody.
thumbFile: Movie - The Lego Movie [265055].images\The Lego Movie [265055].thumb.jpg

title: The Lego Movie 2: The Second Part
summary: It's been five years since everything was awesome and the citizens are facing the huge new threat of Lego Duplo, invaders from outer space, wrecking everything faster than they can rebuild.
tagline: They come in pieces.
thumbFile: Movie - The Lego Movie 2_ The Second Part [265061].images\The Lego Movie 2_ The Second Part [265061].thumb.jpg

title: Lemonade Mouth
summary: "Lemonade Mouth" tells kids and tweens that building your confidence rocks and finding your destiny rules. The story follows five disparate high school students - Olivia (Bridgit Mendler), Mo (Naomi Scott), Charlie (Blake Michael), Stella (Hayley Kiyoko), and Wen (Adam Hicks) who meet in detention. They realize they are destined to rock, and ultimately form a band that becomes a champion for students sidelined by the high school elite.
tagline: Poets, geniuses, revolutionaries.
thumbFile: Movie - Lemonade Mouth [263996].images\Lemonade Mouth [263996].thumb.jpg

title: Lights Out
summary: Rebecca must unlock the terror behind her little brother's experiences that once tested her sanity, bringing her face to face with a supernatural spirit attached to their mother.
tagline: You were right to be afraid of the dark.
thumbFile: Movie - Lights Out [267837].images\Lights Out [267837].thumb.jpg

title: Lilo & Stitch
summary: A young and parentless girl adopts a 'dog' from the local pound, completely unaware that it's supposedly a dangerous scientific experiment that's taken refuge on Earth and is now hiding from its creator and those who see it as a menace.
tagline: There's one in every family.
thumbFile: Movie - Lilo _ Stitch [263999].images\Lilo _ Stitch [263999].thumb.jpg

title: Lilo & Stitch 2: Stitch Has a Glitch
titleSort: Lilo & Stitch 2: Stitch Has a Glitch
summary: Now, we find the rowdy extraterrestrial getting used to life with his new ʻohana. However, a malfunction in the ultimate creation of Dr. Jumba soon emerges, which reinstates his destructive programming and threatens to both ruin his friendship with Lilo and to short him out for good!
thumbFile: Movie - Lilo _ Stitch 2_ Stitch Has a Glitch [264000].images\Lilo _ Stitch 2_ Stitch Has a Glitch [264000].thumb.jpg

title: The Lion King
summary: A young lion prince is cast out of his pride by his cruel uncle, who claims he killed his father. While the uncle rules with an iron paw, the prince grows up beyond the Savannah, living by a philosophy: No worries for the rest of your days. But when his past comes to haunt him, the young prince must decide his fate: Will he remain an outcast or face his demons and become what he needs to be?
tagline: The greatest adventure of all is finding our place in the Circle of Life.
thumbFile: Movie - The Lion King [265072].images\The Lion King [265072].thumb.jpg

title: The Little Mermaid
summary: This colorful adventure tells the story of an impetuous mermaid princess named Ariel who falls in love with the very human Prince Eric and puts everything on the line for the chance to be with him. Memorable songs and characters -- including the villainous sea witch Ursula.
tagline: Somewhere under the sea and beyond your imagination is an adventure in fantasy.
thumbFile: Movie - The Little Mermaid [265076].images\The Little Mermaid [265076].thumb.jpg

title: Little Nicky
summary: When somebody's mother is an angel and his father is the devil, life can be really confusing. For a sweet boy like Little Nicky, it just got a whole lot worse. His two evil brothers Adrian and Cassius have just escaped from Hell and are wreaking havoc on an unsuspecting earth. His dad is disintegrating and it's up to Nicky to save him and all of a humanity by midnight before one of his brothers becomes the new Satan.
tagline: If your father was the Devil and your mother was an angel, you'd be messed up too.
thumbFile: Movie - Little Nicky [264011].images\Little Nicky [264011].thumb.jpg

title: The Little Rascals
summary: Alfalfa is wooing Darla and his "He-Man-Woman-Hating" friends attempt to sabotage the relationship.
tagline: Mischief loves company.
thumbFile: Movie - The Little Rascals [265077].images\The Little Rascals [265077].thumb.jpg

title: The Longest Yard
summary: Prison inmates form a football team to challenge the prison guards.
tagline: If you can't get out, get even.
thumbFile: Movie - The Longest Yard [265085].images\The Longest Yard [265085].thumb.jpg

title: The Lorax
summary: A 12-year-old boy searches for the one thing that will enable him to win the affection of the girl of his dreams. To find it he must discover the story of the Lorax, the grumpy yet charming creature who fights to protect his world.
tagline: Meet the original force of nature.
thumbFile: Movie - The Lorax [265086].images\The Lorax [265086].thumb.jpg

title: The Lord of the Rings: The Fellowship of the Ring
titleSort: Lord of the Rings: The Fellowship of the Ring
summary: Young hobbit Frodo Baggins, after inheriting a mysterious ring from his uncle Bilbo, must leave his home in order to keep it from falling into the hands of its evil creator. Along the way, a fellowship is formed to protect the ringbearer and make sure that the ring arrives at its final destination: Mt. Doom, the only place where it can be destroyed.
tagline: One ring to rule them all.
thumbFile: Movie - The Lord of the Rings_ The Fellowship of the Ring [265089].images\The Lord of the Rings_ The Fellowship of the Ring [265089].thumb.jpg

title: The Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King
titleSort: Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King
summary: The final confrontation between the forces of good and evil fighting for control of the future of Middle-earth. Frodo and Sam reach Mordor in their quest to destroy the One Ring, while Aragorn leads the forces of good against Sauron's evil army at the stone city of Minas Tirith.
tagline: There can be no triumph without loss. No victory without suffering. No freedom without sacrifice.
thumbFile: Movie - The Lord of the Rings_ The Return of the King [265090].images\The Lord of the Rings_ The Return of the King [265090].thumb.jpg

title: The Lord of the Rings: The Two Towers
titleSort: Lord of the Rings: The Two Towers
summary: The continuing quest of Frodo and the Fellowship to destroy the One Ring. Frodo and Sam discover they are being followed by the mysterious Gollum. Aragorn, the Elf archer Legolas, and Gimli the Dwarf encounter the besieged Rohan kingdom, whose once great King Theoden has fallen under Saruman's deadly spell.
tagline: The fellowship is broken. The power of darkness grows...
thumbFile: Movie - The Lord of the Rings_ The Two Towers [265095].images\The Lord of the Rings_ The Two Towers [265095].thumb.jpg

title: The Lost City
summary: Reclusive author Loretta Sage writes about exotic places in her popular adventure novels that feature a handsome cover model named Alan. While on tour promoting her new book with Alan, Loretta gets kidnapped by an eccentric billionaire who hopes she can lead him to an ancient city's lost treasure from her latest story. Determined to prove he can be a hero in real life and not just on the pages of her books, Alan sets off to rescue her.
tagline: The adventure is real. The heroes are not.
thumbFile: Movie - The Lost City [265096].images\The Lost City [265096].thumb.jpg

title: The Lost World: Jurassic Park
summary: Four years after Jurassic Park's genetically bred dinosaurs ran amok, multimillionaire John Hammond shocks chaos theorist Ian Malcolm by revealing that he has been breeding more beasties at a secret location. Malcolm, his paleontologist ladylove and a wildlife videographer join an expedition to document the lethal lizards' natural behavior in this action-packed thriller.
tagline: Something has survived.
thumbFile: Movie - The Lost World_ Jurassic Park [265100].images\The Lost World_ Jurassic Park [265100].thumb.jpg

title: Luck
summary: The curtain is pulled back on the millennia-old battle between the organizations of good luck and bad luck that secretly affects everyday lives.
tagline: Sometimes all you need is for everything to go wrong.
thumbFile: Movie - Luck [264013].images\Luck [264013].thumb.jpg

title: Lucy
summary: A woman, accidentally caught in a dark deal, turns the tables on her captors and transforms into a merciless warrior evolved beyond human logic.
tagline: The average person uses 10% of their brain capacity. Imagine what she could do with 100%.
thumbFile: Movie - Lucy [264014].images\Lucy [264014].thumb.jpg

title: The Machine
summary: Bert Kreischer faces a familial crisis and the arrival of his estranged father when the ghost of his booze-soaked past arrives: a murderous mobster hellbent on kidnapping Bert back to the motherland to atone for his crimes. Together, he and his father must retrace the steps of his younger self in the midst of a war between a sociopathic crime family while they attempt to find common ground.
tagline: To be a hero, it takes a lot of gut.
thumbFile: Movie - The Machine [265106].images\The Machine [265106].thumb.jpg

title: Madagascar
summary: A group of animals who have spent all their life in a New York zoo end up in the jungles of Madagascar, and must adjust to living in the wild.
tagline: Someone’s got a zoo loose.
thumbFile: Movie - Madagascar [264016].images\Madagascar [264016].thumb.jpg

title: Madagascar 3: Europe's Most Wanted
summary: Animal pals Alex, Marty, Melman, and Gloria are still trying to make it back to New York's Central Park Zoo. They are forced to take a detour to Europe to find the penguins and chimps who broke the bank at a Monte Carlo casino. When French animal-control officer Capitaine Chantel DuBois picks up their scent, Alex and company are forced to hide out in a traveling circus.
tagline: They Have One Shot to Get Back Home.
thumbFile: Movie - Madagascar 3_ Europe_s Most Wanted [264018].images\Madagascar 3_ Europe_s Most Wanted [264018].thumb.jpg

title: Madagascar: Escape 2 Africa
summary: The Madagascar animals fly back to New York City, but crash-land on an African nature reserve in Kenya, where they meet others of their own kind, and Alex especially discovers his royal heritage as prince of a lion pride.
tagline: Still together, still lost.
thumbFile: Movie - Madagascar_ Escape 2 Africa [264020].images\Madagascar_ Escape 2 Africa [264020].thumb.jpg

title: Major League
summary: When Rachel Phelps inherits the Cleveland Indians from her deceased husband, she's determined to move the team to a warmer climate—but only a losing season will make that possible, which should be easy given the misfits she's hired. Rachel is sure her dream will come true, but she underestimates their will to succeed.
tagline: A comedy with bats and balls.
thumbFile: Movie - Major League [264025].images\Major League [264025].thumb.jpg

title: Major League II
summary: After losing in the ALCS the year before, the Cleveland Indians are determined to make it into the World Series this time! However, they first have to contend with Rachel Phelps again when she buys back the team.
tagline: The dream team is back!
thumbFile: Movie - Major League II [264028].images\Major League II [264028].thumb.jpg

title: Malibu's Most Wanted
summary: A senator arranges for his son, a rich white kid who fancies himself black, to be kidnapped by a couple of black actors pretending to be murderers to try and shock him out of his plans to become a rapper.
tagline: Ever feel like you don't belong?
thumbFile: Movie - Malibu_s Most Wanted [264033].images\Malibu_s Most Wanted [264033].thumb.jpg

title: The Man from Toronto
summary: In a case of mistaken identity, the world’s deadliest assassin, known as the Man from Toronto, and a New York City screw-up are forced to team up after being confused for each other at a rental cabin.
tagline: Hitman meets dead man.
thumbFile: Movie - The Man from Toronto [265111].images\The Man from Toronto [265111].thumb.jpg

title: Man of Steel
summary: A young boy learns that he has extraordinary powers and is not of this Earth. As a young man, he journeys to discover where he came from and what he was sent here to do. But the hero in him must now emerge if he is to save the world from annihilation and become the symbol of hope for all mankind.
tagline: You will believe that a man can fly.
thumbFile: Movie - Man of Steel [264035].images\Man of Steel [264035].thumb.jpg

title: The Many Adventures of Winnie the Pooh
titleSort: Many Adventures of Winnie the Pooh
summary: Pooh, a bear of very little brain, and all his friends in the Hundred Acre Wood sing their way through adventures that encompass honey, bees, bouncing, balloons, Eeyore's birthday, floods, and Pooh sticks.
tagline: Hip Hip Poohray!
thumbFile: Movie - The Many Adventures of Winnie the Pooh [265112].images\The Many Adventures of Winnie the Pooh [265112].thumb.jpg

title: Masterminds
summary: A guard at an armored car company in the Southern U.S. organizes one of the biggest bank heists in American history. Based on the October 1997 Loomis Fargo robbery.
tagline: What Would You Do With $17 Million?
thumbFile: Movie - Masterminds [264037].images\Masterminds [264037].thumb.jpg

title: Matilda
summary: A girl gifted with a keen intellect and psychic powers uses both to get even with her callous family and free her kindly schoolteacher from the tyrannical grip of a sadistic headmistress.
tagline: A little magic goes a long way.
thumbFile: Movie - Matilda [264040].images\Matilda [264040].thumb.jpg

title: The Matrix
summary: When a beautiful stranger leads computer hacker Neo to a forbidding underworld, he discovers the shocking truth--the life he knows is the elaborate deception of an evil cyber-intelligence.
tagline: The fight for the future begins.
thumbFile: Movie - The Matrix [265115].images\The Matrix [265115].thumb.jpg

title: The Maze Runner
summary: Set in a post-apocalyptic world, young Thomas is deposited in a community of boys after his memory is erased, soon learning they're all trapped in a maze that will require him to join forces with fellow “runners” for a shot at escape.
tagline: Remember. Survive. Run.
thumbFile: Movie - The Maze Runner [265117].images\The Maze Runner [265117].thumb.jpg

title: Maze Runner: The Death Cure
summary: Thomas leads his group of escaped Gladers on their final and most dangerous mission yet. To save their friends, they must break into the legendary Last City, a WCKD-controlled labyrinth that may turn out to be the deadliest maze of all. Anyone who makes it out alive will get answers to the questions the Gladers have been asking since they first arrived in the maze.
tagline: The end will be WCKD
thumbFile: Movie - Maze Runner_ The Death Cure [264042].images\Maze Runner_ The Death Cure [264042].thumb.jpg

title: Maze Runner: The Scorch Trials
summary: The second chapter of the epic "Maze Runner" saga. Thomas (Dylan O'Brien) and his fellow Gladers face their greatest challenge yet: searching for clues about the mysterious and powerful organization known as WCKD. Their journey takes them to the Scorch, a desolate landscape filled with unimaginable obstacles. Teaming up with resistance fighters, the Gladers take on WCKD's vastly superior forces and uncover its shocking plans for them all.
tagline: The Maze Was Just the Beginning.
thumbFile: Movie - Maze Runner_ The Scorch Trials [264050].images\Maze Runner_ The Scorch Trials [264050].thumb.jpg

title: Me Time
summary: When a stay-at-home dad who dedicates all his time to his children is persuaded to take time off for himself, he gets mixed up in the wild shenanigans of his childhood friend who's celebrating his 44th birthday.
tagline: This is not what he had in mind.
thumbFile: Movie - Me Time [264051].images\Me Time [264051].thumb.jpg

title: Meet Dave
summary: A crew of miniature aliens operate a spaceship that has a human form. While trying to save their planet, the aliens encounter a new problem, as their ship becomes smitten with an Earth woman.
tagline: There's a whole other world going on inside of him.
thumbFile: Movie - Meet Dave [264054].images\Meet Dave [264054].thumb.jpg

title: The Meg
summary: A group of scientists exploring the Marianas Trench encounter the largest marine predator that has ever existed - the Megalodon.
tagline: Pleased to eat you.
thumbFile: Movie - The Meg [265120].images\The Meg [265120].thumb.jpg

title: Meg 2: The Trench
summary: An exploratory dive into the deepest depths of the ocean of a daring research team spirals into chaos when a malevolent mining operation threatens their mission and forces them into a high-stakes battle for survival.
tagline: Back for seconds.
thumbFile: Movie - Meg 2_ The Trench [264056].images\Meg 2_ The Trench [264056].thumb.jpg

thumbFile: Movie - Pirates of the Caribbean_ On Stranger Tides [264235].images\Pirates of the Caribbean_ On Stranger Tides [264235].thumb.jpg

title: Pirates of the Caribbean: The Curse of the Black Pearl
titleSort: Pirates of the Caribbean: The Curse of the Black Pearl

tagline: Prepare to be blown out of the water.
thumbFile: Movie - Pirates of the Caribbean_ The Curse of the Black Pearl [264236].images\Pirates of the Caribbean_ The Curse of the Black Pearl [264236].thumb.jpg

thumbFile: Movie - Pitch Perfect 3 [264245].images\Pitch Perfect 3 [264245].thumb.jpg

summary: An English soldier and the daughter of an Algonquin chief share a romance when English colonists invade seventeenth century Virginia.
tagline: An American legend comes to life.
thumbFile: Movie - Pocahontas [264248].images\Pocahontas [264248].thumb.jpg

title: Pocahontas 2: Journey to a New World (1998) (V)
titleSort: Pocahontas 2: Journey to a New World (1998) (V)
originalTitle: Pocahontas II: Journey to a New World
summary: When news of John Smith's death reaches America, Pocahontas is devastated. She sets off to London with John Rolfe, to meet with the King of England on a diplomatic mission: to create peace and respect between the two great lands. However, Governor Ratcliffe is still around; he wants to return to Jamestown and take over, no matter what the cost. He will stop at nothing to discredit the young princess.
tagline: A New Journey Begins!
thumbFile: Movie - Pocahontas 2_ Journey to a New World (1998) (V) [264249].images\Pocahontas 2_ Journey to a New World (1998) (V) [264249].thumb.jpg

tagline: This holiday season... believe.
thumbFile: Movie - The Polar Express [265159].images\The Polar Express [265159].thumb.jpg

But the Beast is not to be put off so easily and appears in a ghostly apparition as the Reverend Kane, a religeous zealot responsible for the deaths of his many followers. His goal is simple - he wants the angelic Carol Anne.
tagline: “They're back”
thumbFile: Movie - Poltergeist II_ The Other Side [265506].images\Poltergeist II_ The Other Side [265506].thumb.jpg

title: Poltergeist III
summary: Carol Anne has been sent to live with her Aunt and Uncle in an effort to hide her from the clutches of the ghostly Reverend Kane, but he tracks her down and terrorises her in her relatives' appartment in a tall glass building. Will he finally achieve his target and capture Carol Anne again, or will Tangina be able, yet again, to thwart him?
tagline: No matter where Carol Ann goes...she never goes alone.
thumbFile: Movie - Poltergeist III [265509].images\Poltergeist III [265509].thumb.jpg

title: Pooh's Grand Adventure: The Search for Christopher Robin
titleSort: Pooh's Grand Adventure: The Search for Christopher Robin
summary: Winnie the Pooh and Christopher Robin are best friends who wish they could be together forever. However Christopher Robin needs to go to school. Christopher Robin has trouble telling Pooh that they will be separated, so he leaves him a note. Pooh, misunderstanding and believing that Christopher Robin has gone to Skull and needs his help launches a rescue mission with the help of Rabbit, Tigger, and Piglet.
tagline: The All - New Movie
thumbFile: Movie - Pooh_s Grand Adventure_ The Search for Christopher Robin [264254].images\Pooh_s Grand Adventure_ The Search for Christopher Robin [264254].thumb.jpg

title: Practical Magic

thumbFile: Movie - Practical Magic [264259].images\Practical Magic [264259].thumb.jpg

title: Predator
summary: A team of commandos on a mission in a Central American jungle find themselves hunted by an extraterrestrial warrior.
tagline: Soon the hunt will begin.
thumbFile: Movie - Predator [264265].images\Predator [264265].thumb.jpg

title: The Predator

Now, the universe's most lethal hunters are stronger, smarter and deadlier than ever before, having genetically upgraded themselves with DNA from other species. When a young boy accidentally triggers their return to Earth, only a ragtag crew of ex-soldiers and a disgruntled science teacher can prevent the end of the human race.
tagline: The hunt has evolved.
thumbFile: Movie - The Predator [265161].images\The Predator [265161].thumb.jpg

title: Predator 2
summary: The Predator returns to Earth, this time to stake a claim on the war-torn streets of a dystopian Los Angeles.

title: Predators
summary: A group of elite warriors parachute into an unfamiliar jungle and are hunted by members of a merciless alien race.
tagline: They are the most dangerous killers on the planet. But this is not our planet.
thumbFile: Movie - Predators [264269].images\Predators [264269].thumb.jpg

title: Prey

When danger threatens her camp, she sets out to protect her people. The prey she stalks: a highly evolved alien predator with a technically advanced arsenal.
tagline: They hunt to live. It lives to hunt.
thumbFile: Movie - Prey [264271].images\Prey [264271].thumb.jpg

thumbFile: Movie - The Princess and the Frog [265167].images\The Princess and the Frog [265167].thumb.jpg

summary: In this enchantingly cracked fairy tale, the beautiful Princess Buttercup and the dashing Westley must overcome staggering odds to find happiness amid six-fingered swordsmen, murderous princes, Sicilians and rodents of unusual size. tagline: It's as real as the feelings you feel.
thumbFile: Movie - The Princess Bride [265169].images\The Princess Bride [265169].thumb.jpg

title: Princess Protection Program
summary: When a tiny country is invaded by a dictator, a young princess (later known as Rosie) is taken into custody by the Princess Protection Program. She is whisked away to rural Louisiana where she must learn the ins and outs of behaving like a normal American teenager. In the process of adapting to her new life, Rosie gives her new friend and roommate, Carter, a few lessons in how to act with royal aplomb.
tagline: Royality meets reality.
thumbFile: Movie - Princess Protection Program [264273].images\Princess Protection Program [264273].thumb.jpg

thumbFile: Movie - Project Power [264275].images\Project Power [264275].thumb.jpg

But when his best friend Costa starts calling radio stations and putting ads up on Craigslist, you can be sure that this party is going to get really out of hand really fast.
tagline: The party you've only dreamed about.
thumbFile: Movie - Project X [264278].images\Project X [264278].thumb.jpg

tagline: You won't know the facts until you've seen the fiction.
thumbFile: Movie - Pulp Fiction [264280].images\Pulp Fiction [264280].thumb.jpg

title: The Punisher

Now serving as judge, jury, and executioner, he's a new kind of vigilante out to wage a one man war against those who have done him wrong.
tagline: There is no justice, there is only revenge.
thumbFile: Movie - The Punisher [265170].images\The Punisher [265170].thumb.jpg

summary: Given the country's overcrowded prisons, the U.S. government begins to allow 12-hour periods of time in which all illegal activity is legal. During one of these free-for-alls, a family must protect themselves from a home invasion.
tagline: One night a year, all crime is legal.
thumbFile: Movie - The Purge [265175].images\The Purge [265175].thumb.jpg

summary: A couple are driving home when their car breaks down just as the Purge commences. Meanwhile, a police sergeant goes out into the streets to get revenge on the man who killed his son, and a mother and daughter run from their home after assailants destroy it. The five people meet up as they attempt to survive the night in Los Angeles.
tagline: Welcome to America where one night a year all crime is legal
thumbFile: Movie - The Purge_ Anarchy [265180].images\The Purge_ Anarchy [265180].thumb.jpg

summary: Two years after choosing not to kill the man who killed his son, former police sergeant Leo Barnes has become head of security for Senator Charlene Roan, the front runner in the next Presidential election due to her vow to eliminate the Purge. On the night of what should be the final Purge, a betrayal from within the government forces Barnes and Roan out onto the street where they must fight to survive the night.
tagline: Keep America great
thumbFile: Movie - The Purge_ Election Year [265183].images\The Purge_ Election Year [265183].thumb.jpg

summary: A struggling salesman takes custody of his son as he's poised to begin a life-changing professional career.
tagline: For his son, one man will reach for the impossible.
thumbFile: Movie - The Pursuit of Happyness [265186].images\The Pursuit of Happyness [265186].thumb.jpg

summary: An outlaw cat, his childhood egg-friend, and a seductive thief kitty set out in search for the eggs of the fabled Golden Goose to clear his name, restore his lost honor, and regain the trust of his mother and town.
tagline: Live for danger. Fight for justice. Pray for mercy.
thumbFile: Movie - Puss in Boots [264284].images\Puss in Boots [264284].thumb.jpg

title: Puss in Boots: The Last Wish
titleSort: Puss in Boots: The Last Wish
summary: When Puss in Boots discovers that his passion for adventure has taken its toll and he has burned through eight of his nine lives, he launches an epic journey to restore them by finding the mythical Last Wish.
tagline: Every legend comes to an end.
thumbFile: Movie - Puss in Boots_ The Last Wish [264285].images\Puss in Boots_ The Last Wish [264285].thumb.jpg

title: Puss in Boots: The Three Diablos
titleSort: Puss in Boots: The Three Diablos
summary: The infamous French thief The Whisperer has stolen a princess' ruby and Puss in Boots is on a mission to recover the precious stone. But Puss must somehow first tame The Three Diablos, three cute little kittens who were The Whisperer's henchmen, before they endanger the mission in this purrfectly charming comedy adventure.
thumbFile: Movie - Puss in Boots_ The Three Diablos [264293].images\Puss in Boots_ The Three Diablos [264293].thumb.jpg

title: R.I.P.D.
summary: In the afterlife, Nick Walker, a detective who used to work for the Boston Police Department, is hired by a director of a group of deceased police officers to fight against the renegade ghosts.
tagline: To protect and serve the living.
thumbFile: Movie - R.I.P.D. [264297].images\R.I.P.D. [264297].thumb.jpg

tagline: The race is on.
thumbFile: Movie - Race to Witch Mountain [264304].images\Race to Witch Mountain [264304].thumb.jpg

title: Raiders of the Lost Ark
summary: When Dr. Indiana Jones – the tweed-suited professor who just happens to be a celebrated archaeologist – is hired by the government to locate the legendary Ark of the Covenant, he finds himself up against the entire Nazi regime.
tagline: If adventure has a name, it must be Indiana Jones!
thumbFile: Movie - Raiders of the Lost Ark [264305].images\Raiders of the Lost Ark [264305].thumb.jpg

tagline: A journey through understanding and fellowship.
thumbFile: Movie - Rain Man [264306].images\Rain Man [264306].thumb.jpg

summary: Taking place six years after saving the arcade from Turbo's vengeance, the Sugar Rush arcade cabinet has broken, forcing Ralph and Vanellope to travel to the Internet via the newly-installed Wi-Fi router in Litwak's Arcade to retrieve the piece capable of saving the game.
tagline: Who Broke the Internet?
thumbFile: Movie - Ralph Breaks the Internet [264311].images\Ralph Breaks the Internet [264311].thumb.jpg

title: Rambo

tagline: Live for nothing, or die for something.
thumbFile: Movie - Rambo [264312].images\Rambo [264312].thumb.jpg

summary: Combat has taken its toll on Rambo, but he's finally begun to find inner peace in a monastery. When Rambo's friend and mentor Col. Trautman asks for his help on a top secret mission to Afghanistan, Rambo declines but must reconsider when Trautman is captured.

thumbFile: Movie - Rambo III [264325].images\Rambo III [264325].thumb.jpg

title: Rambo: First Blood Part II
summary: Rambo returns to the jungles of Vietnam on a mission to infiltrate an enemy base-camp and rescue the American POWs still held captive there.
tagline: No man, no law, no war can stop him.
thumbFile: Movie - Rambo_ First Blood Part II [264324].images\Rambo_ First Blood Part II [264324].thumb.jpg

tagline: Everyone has one more fight in them
thumbFile: Movie - Rambo_ Last Blood [264326].images\Rambo_ Last Blood [264326].thumb.jpg

thumbFile: Movie - Ramona and Beezus [264331].images\Ramona and Beezus [264331].thumb.jpg

After a car accident, he winds up in an old western town called Dirt. What this town needs the most is water, but they also need a hero and a sheriff. The thirsty Rango instantly takes on the role of both and selfishly agrees to take on the case of their missing water.

thumbFile: Movie - Rango [264335].images\Rango [264335].thumb.jpg

summary: A Las Vegas casino magnate determined to find a new avenue for wagering sets up a race for money.
tagline: 563 miles. 9 people. $2 million. 1001 problems!
thumbFile: Movie - Rat Race [264337].images\Rat Race [264337].thumb.jpg

The only problem is, Remy is a rat. When he winds up in the sewer beneath one of Paris' finest restaurants, the rodent gourmet finds himself ideally placed to realize his dream.
tagline: He's dying to become a chef.
thumbFile: Movie - Ratatouille [264341].images\Ratatouille [264341].thumb.jpg

Now, 500 years later, those same monsters have returned, and it's up to a lone warrior to track down the last dragon and stop the Druun for good.

thumbFile: Movie - Raya and the Last Dragon [264342].images\Raya and the Last Dragon [264342].thumb.jpg

tagline: A killer game of hide and seek.
thumbFile: Movie - Ready or Not [264347].images\Ready or Not [264347].thumb.jpg

summary: When the creator of a virtual reality called the OASIS dies, he makes a posthumous challenge to all OASIS users to find his Easter Egg, which will give the finder his fortune and control of his world.
tagline: A better reality awaits.
thumbFile: Movie - Ready Player One [264349].images\Ready Player One [264349].thumb.jpg

summary: Charlie Kenton is a washed-up fighter who retired from the ring when robots took over the sport. After his robot is trashed, he reluctantly teams up with his estranged son to rebuild and train an unlikely contender.
tagline: Courage is stronger than steel.
thumbFile: Movie - Real Steel [264352].images\Real Steel [264352].thumb.jpg

summary: An Interpol-issued Red Notice is a global alert to hunt and capture the world's most wanted. But when a daring heist brings together the FBI's top profiler and two rival criminals, there's no telling what will happen.

thumbFile: Movie - Red Notice [264357].images\Red Notice [264357].thumb.jpg

Will it work? Can Rigby tell the truth even if it will cost him and Mordecai their friendship?
tagline: Save the universe from yourselves or you're fired!
thumbFile: Movie - Regular Show_ The Movie [264359].images\Regular Show_ The Movie [264359].thumb.jpg

summary: As Halloweentown prepares to celebrate its 1,000th anniversary, Marnie Piper and her brother Dylan return to Witch University, where trouble is in session from the Sinister Sisters and from someone who's plotting to use Marnie's powers for evil.
tagline: Unlock The Ultimate Secret This October!
thumbFile: Movie - Return to Halloweentown [264366].images\Return to Halloweentown [264366].thumb.jpg

title: Ride Along
summary: Ben must prove he is good enough to date cop James' sister, so he volunteers to go on a "Ride Along" with him to show that he is not weak and will do whatever he must to get James' approval. But along the way, he runs into some obstacles that he must somehow overcome, and he finds very funny ways.
tagline: Propose to this cop's sister? Rookie mistake.
thumbFile: Movie - Ride Along [264371].images\Ride Along [264371].thumb.jpg

title: Ride Along 2
summary: As his wedding day approaches, Ben heads to Miami with his soon-to-be brother-in-law James to bring down a drug dealer who's supplying the dealers of Atlanta with product.
tagline: The brothers-in-law are back
thumbFile: Movie - Ride Along 2 [264374].images\Ride Along 2 [264374].thumb.jpg

title: The Ridiculous 6
summary: A white man, Tommy, raised by Indians is approached by his long lost father who tells him he needs $50,000 or he'll die at the hands of his former gang. Tommy goes on an incredible and ridiculous journey picking up his other 5 new brothers on the way in a race to save their dad.
tagline: The Wild West has met its match.
thumbFile: Movie - The Ridiculous 6 [265190].images\The Ridiculous 6 [265190].thumb.jpg

title: Rim of the World
summary: Four misfit campers must band together and conquer their fears in order to save the world during an alien invasion.
tagline: Saving the world is alien to them
thumbFile: Movie - Rim of the World [264376].images\Rim of the World [264376].thumb.jpg

title: The Ring

There is an urban legend about this tape: the viewer will die seven days after watching it. If the legend is correct, Rachel will have to run against time to save her son's and her own life.
tagline: Before you die, you see the Ring.
thumbFile: Movie - The Ring [265520].images\The Ring [265520].thumb.jpg

title: The Ring Two
summary: A high school student named Jake tries to make his girlfriend Emily watch a cursed tape. But then Jake finds out that Emily covered her eyes and didn't watch the tape, and then Jake is killed by Samara Morgan (from the first The Ring movie). Rachel Keller learns of Jake's death and finds his twisted body in the back of an ambulance. Rachel then realizes she once again has to save her son Aidan from Samara the evil ghost child.
tagline: Fear comes full circle
thumbFile: Movie - The Ring Two [265524].images\The Ring Two [265524].thumb.jpg

title: Rings
summary: Julia becomes worried about her boyfriend, Holt, when he explores the dark urban legend of a mysterious video said to kill the watcher seven days after viewing. She sacrifices herself to save her boyfriend and in doing so makes a horrifying discovery: there is a "movie within the movie" that no one has ever seen before.
tagline: First you watch it. Then you die.
thumbFile: Movie - Rings [265512].images\Rings [265512].thumb.jpg

title: Rise of the Planet of the Apes
titleSort: Rise of the Planet of the Apes
summary: A highly intelligent chimpanzee named Caesar has been living a peaceful suburban life ever since he was born. But when he gets taken to a cruel primate facility, Caesar decides to revolt against those who have harmed him.
tagline: Evolution Becomes Revolution.
thumbFile: Movie - Rise of the Planet of the Apes [264377].images\Rise of the Planet of the Apes [264377].thumb.jpg

title: The Ritual

When one of them is injured, they have no choice but to cut through the forest in order to arrive at the lodge a couple of hours sooner. During a raging rainstorm, they spent the night in a spooky, abandoned house. What awaits them are things they never expect out of this supposedly bonding trip.
tagline: Your darkest dream awaits you.
thumbFile: Movie - The Ritual [265191].images\The Ritual [265191].thumb.jpg

title: Robin Hood
summary: An imaginative Disney version of the Robin Hood legend. Fun and romance abound as the swashbuckling hero of Sherwood Forest and his valiant sidekick plot one daring adventure after another to outwit the greedy Prince John (Sir Peter Ustinov) and his partner as they put the tax squeeze on the poor.
tagline: Meet Robin Hood and his MERRY MENagerie!
thumbFile: Movie - Robin Hood [264386].images\Robin Hood [264386].thumb.jpg

title: RoboCop
