To test their crime-eradicating cyborgs, the company leads street cop Alex Murphy into an armed confrontation with crime lord Boddicker so they can use his body to support their untested RoboCop prototype. But when RoboCop learns of the company's nefarious plans, he turns on his masters.
tagline: Part man, part machine, all cop.
thumbFile: Movie - RoboCop [264388].images\RoboCop [264388].thumb.jpg

title: RoboCop 2
summary: RoboCop returns to protect the citizens of old Detroit but faces a deadly challenge when a rogue OCP member secretly creates a new, evil RoboCop 2.
tagline: He's back to protect the innocent.
thumbFile: Movie - RoboCop 2 [264389].images\RoboCop 2 [264389].thumb.jpg

title: RoboCop 3
summary: Robocop saves the day once more. This time the half man/half robot takes on ruthless developers who want to evict some people on "their" land.
tagline: He's back. Back on line. Back on duty.
thumbFile: Movie - RoboCop 3 [264390].images\RoboCop 3 [264390].thumb.jpg

title: Robots

The group must find a way to defeat the evil that threatens the city and give the company back to its rightful owner.
tagline: The biggest comedy ever assembled!
thumbFile: Movie - Robots [264394].images\Robots [264394].thumb.jpg

title: Rocky
summary: A small-time Philadelphia boxer gets a supremely rare chance to fight the world heavyweight champion in a bout in which he strives to go the distance for his self-respect.
tagline: His whole life was a million-to-one shot.
thumbFile: Movie - Rocky [264395].images\Rocky [264395].thumb.jpg

When he loses a highly publicized virtual boxing match to ex-champ Rocky Balboa, reigning heavyweight titleholder Mason Dixon retaliates by challenging Rocky to a nationally televised, 10-round exhibition bout. To the surprise of his son and friends, Rocky agrees to come out of retirement and face an opponent who's faster, stronger, and thirty years his junior.
tagline: It ain't over 'til it's over.
thumbFile: Movie - Rocky Balboa [264397].images\Rocky Balboa [264397].thumb.jpg

title: Rocky II
summary: After Rocky goes the distance with champ Apollo Creed, both try to put the fight behind them and move on. Rocky settles down with Adrian but can't put his life together outside the ring, while Creed seeks a rematch to restore his reputation. Soon enough, the "Master of Disaster" and the "Italian Stallion" are set on a collision course for a climactic battle that is brutal and unforgettable.
tagline: Once he fought for a dream. Now he's fighting for love!
thumbFile: Movie - Rocky II [264402].images\Rocky II [264402].thumb.jpg

title: Rocky III
summary: Now the world champion, Rocky Balboa is living in luxury and only fighting opponents who pose no threat to him in the ring, until Clubber Lang challenges him to a bout. After taking a pounding from Lang, the humbled champ turns to former bitter rival Apollo Creed for a rematch with Lang.
tagline: The greatest challenge
thumbFile: Movie - Rocky III [264403].images\Rocky III [264403].thumb.jpg

title: Rocky IV
summary: Rocky Balboa accompanies his friend Apollo Creed to the ring in a boxing match against a Russian Boxer named Ivan Drago. Drago is too strong for Creed, and unfortunately kills him in his match. Balboa blames himself for Creed's death and is determined to defeat Drago in a boxing match. He gains the help of Creed's former manager, Duke and travels to U.S.S.R. to take on Drago.
tagline: He's facing the ultimate challenge. And fighting for his life.
thumbFile: Movie - Rocky IV [264407].images\Rocky IV [264407].thumb.jpg

title: Rocky V
summary: A lifetime of taking shots has ended Rocky’s career, and a crooked accountant has left him broke. Inspired by the memory of his trainer, however, Rocky finds glory in training and takes on an up-and-coming boxer.
tagline: In Russia, he fought the greatest fight of his life. Now...where does a champion go when he takes off the gloves?
thumbFile: Movie - Rocky V [264410].images\Rocky V [264410].thumb.jpg

title: Ron's Gone Wrong
summary: The story of Barney, an awkward middle-schooler and Ron, his new walking, talking, digitally-connected device. Ron's malfunctions set against the backdrop of the social media age launch them on a journey to learn about true friendship.
tagline: Best Friend Forever* (*battery life may vary)
thumbFile: Movie - Ron_s Gone Wrong [264412].images\Ron_s Gone Wrong [264412].thumb.jpg

title: Rookie of the Year
summary: When an accident miraculously gives a boy an incredibly powerful pitching arm, he becomes a major league pitcher for the Chicago Cubs.
tagline: The Chicago Cubs needed a miracle... They got Henry Rowengartner.
thumbFile: Movie - Rookie of the Year [264414].images\Rookie of the Year [264414].thumb.jpg

title: Rubber
summary: A group of people gather in the California desert to watch a "film" set in the late 1990s featuring a sentient, homicidal car tire named Robert. The assembled crowd of onlookers watch as Robert becomes obsessed with a beautiful and mysterious woman and goes on a rampage through a desert town.
tagline: Are you TIRED of the expected?
thumbFile: Movie - Rubber [267812].images\Rubber [267812].thumb.jpg

title: Rudolph the Red-Nosed Reindeer
summary: A young reindeer Rudolph lives at the North Pole. His father is one of Santa's reindeer and it is expected that Rudolph will eventually be one too. However, he has a feature which is a setback and causes him to be ostracized: his red nose.
tagline: You might even say it glows!
thumbFile: Movie - Rudolph the Red-Nosed Reindeer [264419].images\Rudolph the Red-Nosed Reindeer [264419].thumb.jpg

title: The Sandlot

tagline: They're more than a team. They're the best buddies in the entire history of the world.
thumbFile: Movie - The Sandlot [265196].images\The Sandlot [265196].thumb.jpg

title: The Sandlot 2
summary: A decade has passed in the small town where the original Sandlot gang banded together during the summer of ’62 to play baseball and battle the Beast. Now, back at the dugout, nine new kids descend on the diamond only to discover that a descendant of the Beast lives in Mr. Mertle’s backyard – a monster of mythical proportions known as 'The Great Fear'.
tagline: A Home Run of Family Fun!
thumbFile: Movie - The Sandlot 2 [265198].images\The Sandlot 2 [265198].thumb.jpg

title: The Sandlot: Heading Home
summary: Successful, arrogant baseball superstar Tommy "Santa" Santorelli travels back in time to 1976 and relives his boyhood days on the sandlot baseball team, and has the chance to this time choose friendship over glory.
thumbFile: Movie - The Sandlot_ Heading Home [265200].images\The Sandlot_ Heading Home [265200].thumb.jpg

title: Sandy Wexler
summary: Sandy Wexler (Adam Sandler) is a talent manager working in Los Angeles in the 1990s, diligently representing a group of eccentric clients on the fringes of show business. His single-minded devotion is put to the test when he falls in love with his newest client, Courtney Clarke, a tremendously talented singer whom he discovers at an amusement park. Over the course of a decade, the two of them play out a star-crossed love story.
thumbFile: Movie - Sandy Wexler [264421].images\Sandy Wexler [264421].thumb.jpg

title: The Santa Clause
summary: On Christmas Eve, divorced dad Scott Calvin and his son discover Santa Claus has fallen off their roof. When Scott takes the reins of the magical sleigh, he finds he is now the new Santa, and must convince a world of disbelievers, including himself.
tagline: What if your dad was Santa Claus?
thumbFile: Movie - The Santa Clause [267862].images\The Santa Clause [267862].thumb.jpg

title: The Santa Clause 2
summary: Better watch out! The big guy in red is coming to town once again. This time, Scott Calvin -- also known as Santa Claus -- finds out there's an obscure clause in his contract requiring him to take on a wife. He has to leave the North Pole to fulfill his obligations, or else he'll be forced to give up his Yuletide gig.
tagline: What's Christmas Fun without some Reindeer Games?
thumbFile: Movie - The Santa Clause 2 [267864].images\The Santa Clause 2 [267864].thumb.jpg

title: The Santa Clause 3: The Escape Clause
summary: Now that Santa Claus/Scott Calvin and Mrs. Claus/Carol Newman Calvin have the North Pole running smoothly, the Counsel of Legendary Figures has called an emergency meeting on Christmas Eve. The evil Jack Frost has been making trouble, looking to take over the holiday. So he launches a plan to sabotage the toy factory and compel Scott to invoke the little-known Escape Clause and wish he'd never become Santa.
tagline: 'Twas the Fight Before Christmas...
thumbFile: Movie - The Santa Clause 3_ The Escape Clause [267873].images\The Santa Clause 3_ The Escape Clause [267873].thumb.jpg

title: Saving Private Ryan
summary: As U.S. troops storm the beaches of Normandy, three brothers lie dead on the battlefield, with a fourth trapped behind enemy lines. Ranger captain John Miller and seven men are tasked with penetrating German-held territory and bringing the boy home.
tagline: The mission is a man.
thumbFile: Movie - Saving Private Ryan [264422].images\Saving Private Ryan [264422].thumb.jpg

title: Saw
summary: Waking up in a bathroom, two men, Adam and Dr. Lawrence Gordon, discover they have been captured by the infamous man known as Jigsaw. The men must escape before time runs out, otherwise, they will face the deadly consequences.
tagline: How much blood would you shed to stay alive?
thumbFile: Movie - Saw [264427].images\Saw [264427].thumb.jpg

title: Saw 3D
summary: As a deadly battle rages over Jigsaw's brutal legacy, a group of Jigsaw survivors gathers to seek the support of self-help guru and fellow survivor Bobby Dagen, a man whose own dark secrets unleash a new wave of terror.
tagline: The traps come alive.
thumbFile: Movie - Saw 3D [264429].images\Saw 3D [264429].thumb.jpg

title: Saw II
summary: Detective Eric Matthews, along with fellow police officers and a SWAT Team, locate Jigsaw's lair and go to arrest him, but discover that his arrest is only a part of Jigsaw's plan. Matthews soon learns that eight people are trapped in an old house and are playing one of Jigsaw's games. One of them is his own son, Daniel Matthews. Eric learns that if he wants to see his son again, he must play one of Jigsaw's games as well.
tagline: Oh yes... There will be blood.
thumbFile: Movie - Saw II [264435].images\Saw II [264435].thumb.jpg

title: Saw III
summary: Jigsaw has disappeared. Along with his new apprentice Amanda, the puppet-master behind the cruel, intricate games that have terrified a community and baffled police has once again eluded capture and vanished. While city detective scrambles to locate him, Doctor Lynn Denlon and Jeff Reinhart are unaware that they are about to become the latest pawns on his vicious chessboard.
tagline: Suffering? You haven't seen anything yet...
thumbFile: Movie - Saw III [264437].images\Saw III [264437].thumb.jpg

title: Saw IV
summary: Despite Jigsaw's death, and in order to save the lives of two of his colleagues, Lieutenant Rigg is forced to take part in a new game, which promises to test him to the limit.
tagline: You thought it was over...but the games have just begun.
thumbFile: Movie - Saw IV [264444].images\Saw IV [264444].thumb.jpg

title: Saw V
summary: Following Jigsaw's grisly demise, Mark Hoffman is commended as a hero, but Agent Strahm is suspicious, and delves into Hoffman's past. Meanwhile, another group of people are put through a series of gruesome tests.
tagline: You won't believe how it ends.
thumbFile: Movie - Saw V [264447].images\Saw V [264447].thumb.jpg

title: Saw VI
summary: Special Agent Strahm is dead, and Detective Hoffman has emerged as the unchallenged successor to Jigsaw's legacy. However, when the FBI draws closer to Hoffman, he is forced to set a game into motion, and Jigsaw's grand scheme is finally understood.
tagline: The game has come full circle.
thumbFile: Movie - Saw VI [264448].images\Saw VI [264448].thumb.jpg

title: Saw X
summary: A sick and desperate John travels to Mexico for a risky and experimental medical procedure in hopes of a miracle cure for his cancer only to discover the entire operation is a scam to defraud the most vulnerable.
tagline: Witness the return of Jigsaw.
thumbFile: Movie - Saw X [264450].images\Saw X [264450].thumb.jpg

title: Scarface
summary: An ambitious and nearly insane violent gangster climbs the ladder of success in the mob, but his weaknesses prove to be his downfall.
tagline: The rise and fall of a power hungry mobster.
thumbFile: Movie - Scarface [264453].images\Scarface [264453].thumb.jpg

title: Scary Movie
summary: A group of teenagers including Cindy Campbell and Bobby Prinze, accidentally hit a man when driving, and dispose of the body, but now they are being stalked by a very recognisable masked killer. The victim count increases, whilst Cindy must survive the carnage that has she has seen in so many films before.
tagline: No mercy. No shame. No sequel.
thumbFile: Movie - Scary Movie [264458].images\Scary Movie [264458].thumb.jpg

title: Scary Movie 2
summary: While the original parodied slasher flicks like Scream, Keenen Ivory Wayans's sequel to Scary Movie takes comedic aim at haunted house movies. A group of students visit a mansion called "Hell House," and murderous high jinks ensue.
tagline: More merciless. More shameless.
thumbFile: Movie - Scary Movie 2 [264459].images\Scary Movie 2 [264459].thumb.jpg

title: Scary Movie 3
summary: In the third installment of the Scary Movie franchise, news anchorwoman Cindy Campbell has to investigate mysterious crop circles and killing video tapes, and help the President stop an alien invasion in the process.
tagline: Great trilogies come in threes.
thumbFile: Movie - Scary Movie 3 [264460].images\Scary Movie 3 [264460].thumb.jpg

title: Scary Movie 4
summary: Cindy finds out the house she lives in is haunted by a little boy and goes on a quest to find out who killed him and why. Also, Alien "Tr-iPods" are invading the world and she has to uncover the secret in order to stop them.
tagline: Bury the grudge. Burn the village.  See the saw.
thumbFile: Movie - Scary Movie 4 [264461].images\Scary Movie 4 [264461].thumb.jpg

title: Scary Movie V
summary: Happily-married couple Dan and Jody begin to notice some bizarre activity once they bring their lost nieces and nephew home. Together, with the advice of a psychic and the aid of numerous surveillance cameras, they must figure out how to get rid of it before it's too late.
tagline: Evil is coming. Bring protection.
thumbFile: Movie - Scary Movie V [264462].images\Scary Movie V [264462].thumb.jpg

title: Schindler's List
summary: Oskar Schindler is a vain and greedy German businessman who becomes an unlikely humanitarian amid the barbaric German Nazi reign when he feels compelled to turn his factory into a refuge for Jews. Based on the true story of Oskar Schindler who managed to save about 1100 Jews from being gassed at the Auschwitz concentration camp, it is a testament to the good in all of us.
tagline: Whoever saves one life, saves the world entire.
thumbFile: Movie - Schindler_s List [264466].images\Schindler_s List [264466].thumb.jpg

title: School of Rock
summary: After being fired from his own rock band, a struggling musician poses as a substitute teacher at a private elementary school. After getting to know his class, he does everything to form a band with them for a competition called "Battle of the Bands". They do everything in order to prepare themselves for the competition without anyone else discovering the real truth.
tagline: He just landed the gig of his life: 5th grade.
thumbFile: Movie - School of Rock [267814].images\School of Rock [267814].thumb.jpg

title: Scooby-Doo
summary: A group of friends are summoned to a mysterious to investigate a series of dark and ghostly events. They discover that there is more than meets the eye. They follow a trail of clues that will lead them to a surprise that they are not prepared for.
tagline: Be afraid. Be kind of afraid.
thumbFile: Movie - Scooby-Doo [264468].images\Scooby-Doo [264468].thumb.jpg

title: Scooby-Doo and the Loch Ness Monster
titleSort: Scooby-Doo and the Loch Ness Monster
summary: While the gang travel to Scotland to visit Daphne's cousin and witness the Highland Games, they find themselves terrorized by the legendary Loch Ness Monster.
tagline: Scooby-Doo! and crew tackle their scariest mystery yet!
thumbFile: Movie - Scooby-Doo and the Loch Ness Monster [264469].images\Scooby-Doo and the Loch Ness Monster [264469].thumb.jpg

title: Scott Pilgrim vs. the World
summary: As bass guitarist for a garage-rock band, Scott Pilgrim has never had trouble getting a girlfriend; usually, the problem is getting rid of them. But when Ramona Flowers skates into his heart, he finds she has the most troublesome baggage of all: an army of ex-boyfriends who will stop at nothing to eliminate him from her list of suitors.
tagline: An epic of epic epicness.
thumbFile: Movie - Scott Pilgrim vs. the World [264472].images\Scott Pilgrim vs. the World [264472].thumb.jpg

title: Scream
summary: A year after the murder of her mother, a teenage girl is terrorized by a masked killer who targets her and her friends by using scary movies as part of a deadly game.
tagline: Someone has taken their love of scary movies one step too far. Solving this mystery is going to be murder.
thumbFile: Movie - Scream [264479].images\Scream [264479].thumb.jpg

title: Scream
summary: 25 years after a streak of brutal murders shocked the quiet town of Woodsboro, Calif., a new killer dons the Ghostface mask and begins targeting a group of teenagers to resurrect secrets from the town's deadly past.
tagline: It's always someone you know.
thumbFile: Movie - Scream [264480].images\Scream [264480].thumb.jpg

title: Scream 2
summary: Two years after the events of Scream, Sidney Prescott and Randy are attending Windsor college. They are trying to get on with their lives...Until a new Ghostface killing spree begins. With the help of Dewey and Gale, Sidney must find out who's behind the murders. As the body count goes up, the list of suspects goes down.
tagline: Someone has taken their love of sequels one step too far.
thumbFile: Movie - Scream 2 [264485].images\Scream 2 [264485].thumb.jpg

title: Scream 3
summary: A new film is currently in production, and a killer is on the loose. The murders draw a reporter, ex-cop, and young woman to the set of the movie inspired by their life. They soon find out that they are dealing with a trilogy, and in a trilogy...anything can happen.
tagline: The most terrifying scream is always the last.
thumbFile: Movie - Scream 3 [264486].images\Scream 3 [264486].thumb.jpg

title: Scream 4
summary: Sidney Prescott, now the author of a self-help book, returns home to Woodsboro on the last stop of her book tour. There she reconnects with Sheriff Dewey and Gale, who are now married, as well as her cousin Jill and her Aunt Kate. Unfortunately, Sidney's appearance also brings about the return of Ghostface, putting Sidney, Gale, and Dewey, along with Jill, her friends, and the whole town of Woodsboro in danger.
tagline: New decade. New rules.
thumbFile: Movie - Scream 4 [264493].images\Scream 4 [264493].thumb.jpg

title: Scream VI
summary: The survivors of the Ghostface killings leave Woodsboro behind and start a fresh chapter in New York City.
tagline: New York. New rules.
thumbFile: Movie - Scream VI [264497].images\Scream VI [264497].thumb.jpg

title: The Secret Life of Pets
summary: In a Manhattan apartment building, Max's life as a favorite pet is turned upside-down, when his owner brings home sloppy mongrel Duke. They must put their quarrels aside when they learn that adorable white bunny Snowball is building an army of lost pets determined to wreak revenge.
tagline: Think this is what they do all day?
thumbFile: Movie - The Secret Life of Pets [265201].images\The Secret Life of Pets [265201].thumb.jpg

title: The Secret Life of Pets 2
summary: Max faces some major changes after his owner Katie gets married and now has a child. On a family trip to the countryside, Max meets a farm dog named Rooster, and both attempt to overcome his fears. Meanwhile, Gidget tries to rescue Max's favorite toy from a cat-packed apartment, and Snowball sets on a mission to free a white tiger named Hu from a circus.
tagline: They still have their secrets.
thumbFile: Movie - The Secret Life of Pets 2 [265204].images\The Secret Life of Pets 2 [265204].thumb.jpg

title: Shark Tale

Being a bottom feeder, Oscar takes advantage of the situation and makes himself look like he killed the finned mobster. Oscar soon comes to realize that his claim may have serious consequences.
tagline: Behind every little fish is a great white lie.
thumbFile: Movie - Shark Tale [264498].images\Shark Tale [264498].thumb.jpg

title: Shaun of the Dead
summary: Shaun (Simon Pegg) doesn't have a very good day, so he decides to turn his life around by getting his ex to take him back, but he times it for right in the middle of what may be a zombie apocalypse. But for him, it's an opportunity to show everyone he knows how useful he is by saving them all. All he has to do is survive, and get his ex back.
tagline: A romantic comedy. With zombies.
thumbFile: Movie - Shaun of the Dead [264499].images\Shaun of the Dead [264499].thumb.jpg

title: Shaun the Sheep Movie
summary: When Shaun decides to take the day off and have some fun, he gets a little more action than he bargained for. A mix up with the Farmer, a caravan and a very steep hill lead them all to the Big City and it's up to Shaun and the flock to return everyone safely to the green grass of home.
tagline: Moving on to Pastures New.
thumbFile: Movie - Shaun the Sheep Movie [264504].images\Shaun the Sheep Movie [264504].thumb.jpg

title: The Shawshank Redemption
summary: Chronicles the experiences of a formerly successful banker as a prisoner in the gloomy jailhouse of Shawshank after being found guilty of a crime he did not commit. The film portrays the man's unique way of dealing with his new, torturous life; along the way he befriends a number of fellow prisoners, most notably a wise long-term inmate named Red.
tagline: Fear can hold you prisoner. Hope can set you free.
thumbFile: Movie - The Shawshank Redemption [265207].images\The Shawshank Redemption [265207].thumb.jpg

title: Shazam!
summary: A newly fostered young boy in search of his mother instead finds unexpected super powers and soon gains a powerful enemy.
tagline: Just say the word.
thumbFile: Movie - Shazam_ [264505].images\Shazam_ [264505].thumb.jpg

title: Shazam! Fury of the Gods
summary: Bestowed with the powers of the gods, Billy Batson and his fellow foster kids are still learning how to juggle teenage life with their adult superhero alter egos. When a vengeful trio of ancient gods arrives on Earth in search of the magic stolen from them long ago, Shazam and his allies get thrust into a battle for their superpowers, their lives, and the fate of the world.
tagline: Oh. My. Gods.
thumbFile: Movie - Shazam_ Fury of the Gods [264509].images\Shazam_ Fury of the Gods [264509].thumb.jpg

title: Sherlock Gnomes
summary: Garden gnomes, Gnomeo and Juliet recruit renowned detective Sherlock Gnomes to investigate the mysterious disappearance of other garden ornaments.
tagline: They're on a mission to bring every gnome home.
thumbFile: Movie - Sherlock Gnomes [264513].images\Sherlock Gnomes [264513].thumb.jpg

title: The Shining
summary: A family heads to an isolated hotel for the winter, where a sinister presence influences the father into violence. At the same time, his psychic son sees horrifying forebodings from both the past and the future.
tagline: A masterpiece of modern horror.
thumbFile: Movie - The Shining [265220].images\The Shining [265220].thumb.jpg

title: Shocking Dark
summary: In a polluted future Venice researchers work to improve the situation. One day, unknown forces start killing them. A team of soldiers and a couple of civilians is sent to investigate. Soon, they encounter strange murderous creatures.
thumbFile: Movie - Shocking Dark [264759].images\Shocking Dark [264759].thumb.jpg

title: Shrek
summary: It ain't easy bein' green -- especially if you're a likable (albeit smelly) ogre named Shrek. On a mission to retrieve a gorgeous princess from the clutches of a fire-breathing dragon, Shrek teams up with an unlikely compatriot -- a wisecracking donkey.
tagline: The greatest fairy tale never told.
thumbFile: Movie - Shrek [264514].images\Shrek [264514].thumb.jpg

title: Shrek 2
summary: Shrek and Fiona travel to the Kingdom of Far Far Away, where Fiona's parents are King and Queen, to celebrate their marriage. When they arrive, they find they are not as welcome as they thought they would be.
tagline: Once upon another time...
thumbFile: Movie - Shrek 2 [264521].images\Shrek 2 [264521].thumb.jpg

title: Shrek Forever After
summary: A bored and domesticated Shrek pacts with deal-maker Rumpelstiltskin to get back to feeling like a real ogre again, but when he's duped and sent to a twisted version of Far Far Away—where Rumpelstiltskin is king, ogres are hunted, and he and Fiona have never met—he sets out to restore his world and reclaim his true love.
tagline: It ain't ogre...til it's ogre.
thumbFile: Movie - Shrek Forever After [264529].images\Shrek Forever After [264529].thumb.jpg

title: Shrek the Third
summary: Reluctantly designated as the heir to the land of Far, Far Away, Shrek hatches a plan to install the rebellious Artie as the new king while Princess Fiona tries to fend off a coup d'état by the jilted Prince Charming.
tagline: He's in for the royal treatment.
thumbFile: Movie - Shrek the Third [267898].images\Shrek the Third [267898].thumb.jpg

title: The Silence of the Lambs
summary: Clarice Starling is a top student at the FBI's training academy.  Jack Crawford wants Clarice to interview Dr. Hannibal Lecter, a brilliant psychiatrist who is also a violent psychopath, serving life behind bars for various acts of murder and cannibalism.  Crawford believes that Lecter may have insight into a case and that Starling, as an attractive young woman, may be just the bait to draw him out.
tagline: To enter the mind of a killer she must challenge the mind of a madman.
thumbFile: Movie - The Silence of the Lambs [265221].images\The Silence of the Lambs [265221].thumb.jpg

title: The Simpsons Movie
summary: After Homer pollutes the town's water supply, Springfield is encased in a gigantic dome by the EPA and the Simpsons are declared fugitives.
tagline: In a time when computer animation gives us worlds of unsurpassed beauty, one film dares to be ugly.
thumbFile: Movie - The Simpsons Movie [265222].images\The Simpsons Movie [265222].thumb.jpg

title: Sing
summary: In a city of humanoid animals, a hustling theater impresario's attempt to save his theater with a singing competition becomes grander than he anticipates even as its finalists find that their lives will never be the same.
tagline: Auditions begin.
thumbFile: Movie - Sing [264530].images\Sing [264530].thumb.jpg

title: Sinister

tagline: Once you see him, nothing can save you.
thumbFile: Movie - Sinister [264533].images\Sinister [264533].thumb.jpg

title: Sinister 2
summary: After a second family moves into a remote house next to an old church where graphic and gruesome murders took place, Courtney Collins and her two sons Zach and Dylan all not only have to avoid their violently abusive dad and husband, but also have to battle an evil force that lies within the very house they moved into. With the help of an ex-deputy they will attempt to race against time to stop the evil forces of the sinister Bughuul..
tagline: Some Things You Can't Unsee.
thumbFile: Movie - Sinister 2 [264534].images\Sinister 2 [264534].thumb.jpg

title: The Sixth Sense
summary: A child psychologist starts treating a young boy with a disturbing secret.
tagline: Not every gift is a blessing.
thumbFile: Movie - The Sixth Sense [265234].images\The Sixth Sense [265234].thumb.jpg

title: Smile
summary: After witnessing a bizarre, traumatic incident involving a patient, a psychiatrist becomes increasingly convinced she is being threatened by an uncanny entity.
tagline: Once you see it, it's too late.
thumbFile: Movie - Smile [264538].images\Smile [264538].thumb.jpg

title: Smile 2
summary: About to embark on a world tour, global pop sensation Skye Riley begins experiencing increasingly terrifying and inexplicable events. Overwhelmed by the escalating horrors and the pressures of fame, Skye is forced to face her past.
tagline: It's the last thing you'll see.
thumbFile: Movie - Smile 2 [266118].images\Smile 2 [266118].thumb.jpg

title: The Smurfs
summary: When the evil wizard Gargamel chases the tiny blue Smurfs out of their village, they tumble from their magical world and into ours -- in fact, smack dab in the middle of Central Park. Just three apples high and stuck in the Big Apple, the Smurfs must find a way to get back to their village before Gargamel tracks them down.
tagline: Smurf Happens.
thumbFile: Movie - The Smurfs [265243].images\The Smurfs [265243].thumb.jpg

title: The Smurfs 2
summary: The Smurfs team up with their human friends to rescue Smurfette, who has been abducted by Gargamel, since she knows a secret spell that can turn the evil sorcerer's newest creation, creatures called "The Naughties", into real Smurfs.
tagline: Get ready to get naughty!
thumbFile: Movie - The Smurfs 2 [265246].images\The Smurfs 2 [265246].thumb.jpg

title: Smurfs: The Lost Village
summary: In this fully animated, all-new take on the Smurfs, a mysterious map sets Smurfette and her friends Brainy, Clumsy and Hefty on an exciting race through the Forbidden Forest leading to the discovery of the biggest secret in Smurf history.
tagline: They were never alone.
thumbFile: Movie - Smurfs_ The Lost Village [264550].images\Smurfs_ The Lost Village [264550].thumb.jpg

title: Snow White and the Seven Dwarfs
titleSort: Snow White and the Seven Dwarfs
summary: A beautiful girl, Snow White, takes refuge in the forest in the house of seven dwarfs to hide from her stepmother, the wicked Queen. The Queen is jealous because she wants to be known as "the fairest in the land," and Snow White's beauty surpasses her own.
tagline: The Happiest, Dopiest, Grumpiest, Sneeziest movie of the year.
thumbFile: Movie - Snow White and the Seven Dwarfs [264551].images\Snow White and the Seven Dwarfs [264551].thumb.jpg

title: Sonic the Hedgehog
summary: Powered with incredible speed, Sonic The Hedgehog embraces his new home on Earth. That is, until Sonic sparks the attention of super-uncool evil genius Dr. Robotnik. Now it’s super-villain vs. super-sonic in an all-out race across the globe to stop Robotnik from using Sonic’s unique power for world domination.
tagline: A whole new speed of hero.
thumbFile: Movie - Sonic the Hedgehog [264553].images\Sonic the Hedgehog [264553].thumb.jpg

title: Sonic the Hedgehog 2
summary: After settling in Green Hills, Sonic is eager to prove he has what it takes to be a true hero. His test comes when Dr. Robotnik returns, this time with a new partner, Knuckles, in search for an emerald that has the power to destroy civilizations. Sonic teams up with his own sidekick, Tails, and together they embark on a globe-trotting journey to find the emerald before it falls into the wrong hands.
tagline: Welcome to the next level.
thumbFile: Movie - Sonic the Hedgehog 2 [264558].images\Sonic the Hedgehog 2 [264558].thumb.jpg

title: Soul
summary: Joe is a middle-school band teacher whose life hasn't quite gone the way he expected. His true passion is jazz. But when he travels to another realm to help someone find their passion, he soon discovers what it means to have soul.
tagline: Everybody has a soul. Joe Gardner is about to find his.

summary: Woody, Buzz Lightyear and the rest of the gang embark on a road trip with Bonnie and a new toy named Forky. The adventurous journey turns into an unexpected reunion as Woody's slight detour leads him to his long-lost friend Bo Peep. As Woody and Bo discuss the old days, they soon start to realize that they're two worlds apart when it comes to what they want from life as a toy.
tagline: Get Ready to Hit the Road
thumbFile: Movie - Toy Story 4 [265319].images\Toy Story 4 [265319].thumb.jpg

title: Transformers
summary: Young teenager Sam Witwicky becomes involved in the ancient struggle between two extraterrestrial factions of transforming robots – the heroic Autobots and the evil Decepticons. Sam holds the clue to unimaginable power and the Decepticons will stop at nothing to retrieve it.
tagline: Their war. Our world.
thumbFile: Movie - Transformers [265321].images\Transformers [265321].thumb.jpg

title: Transformers: Age of Extinction
summary: As humanity picks up the pieces, following the conclusion of "Transformers: Dark of the Moon," Autobots and Decepticons have all but vanished from the face of the planet. However, a group of powerful, ingenious businessman and scientists attempt to learn from past Transformer incursions and push the boundaries of technology beyond what they can control - all while an ancient, powerful Transformer menace sets Earth in his cross-hairs.
tagline: This is not war, it's extinction.
thumbFile: Movie - Transformers_ Age of Extinction [265322].images\Transformers_ Age of Extinction [265322].thumb.jpg

title: Transformers: Dark of the Moon
summary: The Autobots continue to work for NEST, now no longer in secret. But after discovering a strange artifact during a mission in Chernobyl, it becomes apparent to Optimus Prime that the United States government has been less than forthright with them.
tagline: The invasion we always feared. An enemy we never expected.
thumbFile: Movie - Transformers_ Dark of the Moon [265326].images\Transformers_ Dark of the Moon [265326].thumb.jpg

title: Transformers: Revenge of the Fallen
summary: Sam Witwicky leaves the Autobots behind for a normal life. But when his mind is filled with cryptic symbols, the Decepticons target him and he is dragged back into the Transformers' war.
tagline: Revenge is coming.
thumbFile: Movie - Transformers_ Revenge of the Fallen [265327].images\Transformers_ Revenge of the Fallen [265327].thumb.jpg

title: Transformers: The Last Knight
summary: Having left Earth, Optimus Prime finds his dead home planet, Cybertron, and discovers that he was in fact responsible for its destruction. Optimus learns that he can bring Cybertron back to life, but in order to do so, he will need an artifact that is hidden on Earth.

thumbFile: Movie - Transformers_ The Last Knight [265328].images\Transformers_ The Last Knight [265328].thumb.jpg

title: Treasure Planet

tagline: Find your place in the universe.
thumbFile: Movie - Treasure Planet [265332].images\Treasure Planet [265332].thumb.jpg

title: The Truman Show
summary: Every second of every day, from the moment he was born, for the last thirty years, Truman Burbank has been the unwitting star of the longest running, most popular documentary-soap opera in history. The picture-perfect town of Seahaven that he calls home is actually a gigantic soundstage. Truman's friends and family - everyone he meets, in fact - are actors. He lives every moment under the unblinking gaze of thousands of hidden TV cameras.
tagline: On the air. Unaware.
thumbFile: Movie - The Truman Show [265272].images\The Truman Show [265272].thumb.jpg

title: Twitches
summary: Twin witches who were separated at birth and were adopted by two different families meet on their 21st birthday and must use their powers to save the world in which they were born, where their birth mother still lives.
tagline: This Halloween, broomsticks are so not happenin'.
thumbFile: Movie - Twitches [265279].images\Twitches [265279].thumb.jpg

title: Twitches Too
summary: After using their powers to battle the forces of darkness, the sisters settle down to lead normal lives. However, the discovery that their biological father may not be dead, but residing in New York, causes confusion for the pair.
thumbFile: Movie - Twitches Too [265280].images\Twitches Too [265280].thumb.jpg

summary: After a near-fatal plane crash in WWII, Olympian Louis Zamperini spends a harrowing 47 days in a raft with two fellow crewmen before he's caught by the Japanese navy and sent to a prisoner-of-war camp.
tagline: Survival. Resilience. Redemption.
thumbFile: Movie - Unbroken [265760].images\Unbroken [265760].thumb.jpg

Howard must perform a precarious high-wire act, balancing business, family, and encroaching adversaries on all sides in his relentless pursuit of the ultimate win.
tagline: This is how I win.
thumbFile: Movie - Uncut Gems [265343].images\Uncut Gems [265343].thumb.jpg

thumbFile: Movie - Unpregnant [265360].images\Unpregnant [265360].thumb.jpg

thumbFile: Movie - Us [265363].images\Us [265363].thumb.jpg

title: V/H/S/Beyond
summary: Six bloodcurdling tapes unleash horror in a sci-fi inspired hellscape, pushing the boundaries of fear and suspense.
tagline: No safe space.
thumbFile: Movie - V_H_S_Beyond [266119].images\V_H_S_Beyond [266119].thumb.jpg

title: Vacation
summary: The Griswold family's cross-country drive to the Walley World theme park proves to be much more arduous than they ever anticipated.

Needless to say, things don't go quite as planned.
tagline: What could go wrong?
thumbFile: Movie - Vacation [265365].images\Vacation [265365].thumb.jpg

thumbFile: Movie - Vacation Friends 2 [265371].images\Vacation Friends 2 [265371].thumb.jpg

title: Van Wilder
summary: The most popular kid on campus meets a beautiful journalist who makes him realize that maybe he's afraid to graduate.
tagline: Don't Graduate. Celebrate.
thumbFile: Movie - Van Wilder [267872].images\Van Wilder [267872].thumb.jpg

summary: After a faulty interview with the Life Foundation ruins his career, former reporter Eddie Brock's life is in pieces. Six months later, he comes across the Life Foundation again, and he comes into contact with an alien symbiote and becomes Venom, a parasitic antihero.

thumbFile: Movie - Venom [265373].images\Venom [265373].thumb.jpg

Brock attempts to reignite his career by interviewing serial killer Cletus Kasady, who becomes the host of the symbiote Carnage and escapes prison after a failed execution.

thumbFile: Movie - Venom_ Let There Be Carnage [265379].images\Venom_ Let There Be Carnage [265379].thumb.jpg

thumbFile: Movie - WALLE [265381].images\WALLE [265381].thumb.jpg

title: War for the Planet of the Apes

thumbFile: Movie - War for the Planet of the Apes [265382].images\War for the Planet of the Apes [265382].thumb.jpg

thumbFile: Movie - The Waterboy [265278].images\The Waterboy [265278].thumb.jpg

thumbFile: Movie - We_re the Millers [265392].images\We_re the Millers [265392].thumb.jpg

thumbFile: Movie - Where the Wild Things Are [265404].images\Where the Wild Things Are [265404].thumb.jpg

title: Whiskey Tango Foxtrot
summary: A journalist recounts her wartime coverage in Afghanistan.
tagline: From the headlines to the front lines.
thumbFile: Movie - Whiskey Tango Foxtrot [265406].images\Whiskey Tango Foxtrot [265406].thumb.jpg

tagline: They're going deep undercover.
thumbFile: Movie - White Chicks [265408].images\White Chicks [265408].thumb.jpg

thumbFile: Movie - White Men Can_t Jump [265428].images\White Men Can_t Jump [265428].thumb.jpg

tagline: Of all the guys his daughter could have chosen...
thumbFile: Movie - Why Him_ [265429].images\Why Him_ [265429].thumb.jpg

thumbFile: Movie - Winnie the Pooh [265432].images\Winnie the Pooh [265432].thumb.jpg

thumbFile: Movie - The Wizard of Oz [265525].images\The Wizard of Oz [265525].thumb.jpg

title: Wizards of Waverly Place: The Movie

summary: When Alex ruins a family vacation by accidentally casting a horrible spell on her loved ones, Max works overtime to keep his parents from separating while Alex and Justin seek out the "Stone of Dreams" in a desperate race to reverse the curse. If then don't thell disappear forever.

thumbFile: Movie - Wizards of Waverly Place_ The Movie [265436].images\Wizards of Waverly Place_ The Movie [265436].thumb.jpg

thumbFile: Movie - Wonder [265441].images\Wonder [265441].thumb.jpg

thumbFile: Movie - Would You Rather [265442].images\Would You Rather [265442].thumb.jpg

summary: Ralph is tired of playing the role of a bad guy and embarks on a journey to become a video game hero. But he accidentally lets loose a deadly enemy that threatens the entire arcade.

thumbFile: Movie - Zapped [265448].images\Zapped [265448].thumb.jpg

With the help of an astronaut, the boys attempt to return home.

thumbFile: Movie - Zathura_ A Space Adventure [265462].images\Zathura_ A Space Adventure [265462].thumb.jpg

summary: Columbus, Tallahassee, Wichita, and Little Rock move to the American heartland as they face off against evolved zombies, fellow survivors, and the growing pains of the snarky makeshift family.

thumbFile: Movie - Zombieland_ Double Tap [265467].images\Zombieland_ Double Tap [265467].thumb.jpg

Determined to prove herself, Judy jumps at the opportunity to solve a mysterious case. Unfortunately, that means working with Nick Wilde, a wily fox who makes her job even harder.

thumbFile: Movie - Zootopia [265469].images\Zootopia [265469].thumb.jpg
